\id MRK - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG MARK 01 20/3/91 Macnaughtan
\h MAKA
\toc1 Makamaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe
\toc2 Maka
\toc3 Maka
\mt1 Makamaęž‰ wape pieke Pi Seliapoe
\c 1
\s1 Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionimaęž‰ pi waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 3ęž‰1-12, Luku 3ęž‰1-18, Dioni 1ęž‰19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke Yesu Ketiso ipikaęž‰ pi seliapo doe.
\v 2 Do pitaęž‰ hande potopede Aisayamaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa.
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Ya pi mea puaasaęž‰ hali ambaęž‰la tapaalueke. Nakaęž‰ potaęž‰ epeaenaęž‰yeke tapaalueke leekeme.
\q1 
\v 3 Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰ wi alaęž‰me dupa
\q1 Tekehalinaęž‰ potaęž‰ epeaape. Ipikaęž‰ potaęž‰ tikitiki yao epeaape laa wi alaęž‰me
\q1 laa wape piekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Koto wape pieke tupaęž‰ bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionimaęž‰ hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ aęž‰pa hayekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peaaso hataęž‰ pi make walaęž‰tiki piekeme. Dupa leekeme. Hone laęž‰kaęž‰la mina wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki bapitaisi peaalueke. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyaalieke leekeme.
\v 5 Diudia nane haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao make Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao make Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pu haemekeme. Kutupa Diodani ikali paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu kaęž‰laęž‰polo haenaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi peatiki piekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Dionimaęž‰taęž‰ kemolo maęž‰naęž‰ itikimaęž‰ wepieke dau pambaotaęž‰ baęž‰taęž‰idotaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yonkelekemaęž‰ wepiekeeki yameekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ netaęž‰ hombutaęž‰ make boi hapeke make naęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.
\v 7 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ dupa leekeme. Ya hoki nane ipiliaęž‰ halitaęž‰ IĚ± halo tupaęž‰ na halaęž‰ hali ipilieke. Ipikitaęž‰ hali tieke ipilieke. IĚ±taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ epeke hali diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao ipikaęž‰ anke dake pu kaęž‰laęž‰papeketaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 8 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ iki bapitaisi peaasopate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ iki bapitaisi peaalieke leekeme.
\s1 Dionimaęž‰ Yesu bapitaisi peaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 3ęž‰13-17, Luku 3ęž‰21-22)
\p 
\v 9 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke Naęž‰saęž‰tete da minaęž‰paęž‰lao Diodani ikali paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Koto ikali paęž‰taęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ Yesu bapitaisi peaeyekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao opaęž‰liaaso hataęž‰ koto kone oli ya akolopaęž‰pa wiekeeki handaataęž‰ oli Holi Sipitidi make melipu tupaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niaeyekeeki handeekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ ya nane hataęž‰ laęž‰niaeyeke pitaęž‰ dupae. Neketaęž‰ ya pukipiki wekie. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolome laa laęž‰niaeyekeme.
\s1 Sadanimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ la handeekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 4ęž‰1-11, Luku 4ęž‰1-13)
\p 
\v 12 Koto kone Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ Yesu penaęž‰yeke tapaeyekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa Sadanimaęž‰ Yesu la handa haenaęž‰taęž‰ nate hali tieke yaaponaęž‰ Yesu koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yeti hao hayeke alenaęž‰ hayekepate mo enisolo tonumaęž‰ aęž‰pa petelemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane pi waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 4ęž‰12-22, Luku 4ęž‰14-15, 5ęž‰1-11)
\p 
\v 14 Dioni dipula mea pitaeyeke hoki nanetaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane puaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo walaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\v 15 Dupa leekeme. Ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ natee. Ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me laa Hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina wiaataęž‰ do Pi Seliapo hone tulao hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo tunkulu pa ulaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ yopulu hataęž‰ mo Saimono Aęž‰ndutu hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰ tenkinu tieke kiake ikali paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaaso haepekeeki handeekeme. Ipilikitaęž‰ taęž‰peli mu haepeke hali yaapoe.
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka hoki nane tolu hapaęž‰peke leekeme. Kutu pipikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ haliweki mulu pelepe hali yaapo hapenaęž‰ walueke leekeme.
\v 18 Koto leekeeki opua ipilikaęž‰ tenkinumanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao koto kone Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea pepekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ hosiki siki mopate leke puaataęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi Dioni hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ Sepedinaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo ipilikaęž‰ palai kawasonaęž‰ pitaęž‰ tenkinumanu tombulolo haepekeeki handeekeme.
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ handaataęž‰ koto kone Ipupe laa wi leekeme. Koto leekeeki opuataęž‰ mo hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰maęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ ateke Sepedi make mo e pokaemeke haliweki make palai kawasonaęž‰ pitinaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea pepekeme.
\s1 Hali pitieke hoke temoko tolu liekeeki
\r (Luku 4ęž‰31-37)
\p 
\v 21 Kutupa Kapeneami da nane pemekepate koto da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ pi waleekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ waleeke pi opuaataęž‰ leke opo handake wimikime. Wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ walo haemeke tupaęž‰ na waleke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ halimaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ waleeke handa pimikime.
\p 
\v 23 Koto kone pi hotu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰pa hayekepate ipikaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitiekeme.
\v 24 Mo halimaęž‰ dupa eĚ± wi leekeme. Yesuo. Naęž‰saęž‰tete halio. Niki paęž‰taęž‰ eki puluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipe laa Neketaęž‰ niki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipe. Neketaęž‰ handolome. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yako piki halie leekeme.
\v 25 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pea hoke temoko paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pi na leke. Koto hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao opolu bao yopue leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Koto leeke handaa hoke temokomaęž‰ hoke eĚ± wi laęž‰ paleke mo hali mea putuputu liaaso hataęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao opolu baeyekeme.
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikieki dupae. Dotaęž‰ eki haupe laa Panake hau walaęž‰laęž‰ekipe laa Biki ulaęž‰ halimaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ pi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi tunkulaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto kone Kaęž‰lili nane paeyao Yesunaęž‰ biki kende tupaęž‰ wiekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰14-17, Luku 4ęž‰38-41)
\p 
\v 29-30 Yesutaęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da minaęž‰paęž‰lao Diaęž‰mesi Dioni ameĚ±leĚ± mo Saimono Aęž‰ndutu yaaponaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pua hondaęž‰ pambemekepate Saimononaęž‰ meiyeke wandaęž‰taęž‰ ki yeni hapa wiekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo da opolo peeke mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ yeni hapa wiekeeki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la halemekeme.
\v 31 Koto lemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ pua ipikaęž‰ kiki mea tiaaso haenaęž‰ yeni tandeleekeme. Kutupieke handaa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali manunaęž‰ ne yankao haleekeme.
\p 
\v 32-33 Koto dinaęž‰ welealo nate pambolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ yeni taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali make weleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitimiki wandaęž‰hali make paeyao Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku aęž‰paataęž‰ daoni wandaęž‰hali paeyao make Yesu hayeke potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa penke haemekeme.
\v 34 Yeni taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ yeni Yesumaęž‰ tandelaotaęž‰ hoke temokomanu wotu make tolu liaataęž‰ temokomanu ipiki handemeke handaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Pi na lapaęž‰pe laataęž‰ tolu liekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane hataęž‰ pi waleekeeki
\r (Luku 4ęž‰42-44)
\p 
\v 35 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso nate aĚ±iĚ± na opeke haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ tiao pa keneme nane pua hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piekeme.
\v 36-37 Koto ekinaęž‰ Saimono ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ anke teli mea pua handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ neke weitelememe lemekeme.
\v 38 Koto lemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mandane da paęž‰taęž‰manu otaęž‰ pomanaęž‰e. IĚ±maęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ make pi walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ Pa ekipekepe. IĚ±taęž‰ kutu puluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa polomaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 39 Koto laataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili da paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu lutia pomiekeme.
\s1 Kindi yeni hayeke hali homeke Yesumaęž‰ mea tiaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰1-4, Luku 5ęž‰12-16)
\p 
\v 40 Kutupa mo kindi yeni hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa tumiki yotu hao pitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ya loke wamo pea hano lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa honke leekeme.
\v 41 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ eĚ± leeke handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipa moneao wataaso hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ loke koto wamo peaaso handaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 42 Koto leeke koto kone kindi yeni wamo peaeyeketaęž‰ pa kindi yeni na hake hali leke hayekeme.
\v 43 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo hali hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 44 Hone wopu wia puaęž‰peke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi na leke ame do kone mo yeni peao halaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ loke pua walaęž‰peke. Kutupa mo hande Mosesimaęž‰ halaęž‰peke laa waleeke aletaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kindi yeni wamo peaowaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mea halaęž‰peke. Kotaęž‰ koto hautaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 45 Koto laa tapaeyekepate kone mo halimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰tia pomiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handolo haenaęž‰ da puaęž‰peke na yeke handaataęž‰ keneme nane hataęž‰ mandane mandane da wandaęž‰hali ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mombelemekeme.
\c 2
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ kiki anke homaęž‰ pa wieke hali mea tiaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰1-8, Luku 5ęž‰17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Nate mandaneeki hao Yesumaęž‰ Kapeneami da paęž‰taęž‰ pa pua haenaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pa aęž‰pa halaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 2 Kotoeki opua wandaęž‰hali wopu pua mombola tumbulu baemeke handaa da paęž‰taęž‰ waleke na wiekeme. Potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ make waleke na wiekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo haenaęž‰ tonkopu haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ kiki anke homaęž‰ pa wieke some homeke meatia epemekeme.
\v 4 Ipulu hataęž‰ handemekepate wandaęž‰hali wopu haemeke handaataęž‰ Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ mea tia puaęž‰peke na yaalo hataęž‰ da holu akolo puluekemaęž‰ aęž‰meimikime. Kutupa kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ wiaotaęž‰ mo hande kiki anke homaęž‰ pa wieke some tili tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mea lopaęž‰niaemekeme.
\v 5 Kutupieketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki handaataęž‰ mo homaęž‰ pa wieke some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya wekio. Nakaęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ pa paeyaasome leekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto leekepate mandane wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone weimikime.
\v 7 Do halimaęž‰ do alaęž‰ pitaęž‰ eki epi alo halaęž‰pe. Ipikaęž‰ pimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki lo hoeyaasaęž‰me hone wia Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke hoke haumanu pa paeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone wimikime.
\p 
\v 8 Koto kone Yesu ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone mo haliwekinaęž‰ hone wimiki ekimanu handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke koto hone witeleme ekimanu weitelemepe leekeme.
\v 9 Eki epi aloeki yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe laa kiki anke homaęž‰ pa ulaęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hoke hau paeyao paeyaalome aloeki yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe o Tiae. Nakaęž‰ tili meatia pue aloeki yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme. Hando ekipe laa
\v 10 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handoemenaęž‰yeke Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke IĚ±taęž‰ hoke haumanu pa paeyaasaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ hali halome laataęž‰ kiki anke homaęž‰ pa wieke some paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 11 Neke paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Tiao. Nakaęž‰ tili meatia da puaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Koto leeke handaa mo hali tiaeyekeme. Koto kone ipikaęž‰ tili tambaęž‰ mea mina paeyaomaęž‰ handolo haenaęž‰ hama peekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyao alotaęž‰ Dupitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na handolomaęž‰ haue lemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Lipae wi leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰9-13, Luku 5ęž‰27-32)
\p 
\v 13 Yesutaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane tunkulu pa ulaęž‰ ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la puaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua mombelemeke handaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pi waleekeme.
\v 14 Pi wala pulu hataęž‰ Aęž‰lopiaęž‰sinaęž‰ eiyeke Lipaetaęž‰ mo dakisi mani mu hayeke alenaęž‰ pitinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ handa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka hoki nane teli mea aęž‰paęž‰peke leeke handaa Lipaemaęž‰ tiao Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea peekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ Lipaenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ne nalo pitinaęž‰ dakisi mani mu haemeke haliweki wopu make hoke haliweki wopu make Yesu ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ pitimikime. Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea epeme ekinaęž‰ pitimikime.
\v 16 Kutupa mandane wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Paęž‰tisi haliweki kone Yesutaęž‰ mo dakisi mu haemeke haliweki make hoke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ne nalo pitimikieki handolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke Yesumaęž‰ dakisi mani mu haleme haliweki mo hoke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ne no pilimipe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ koto lemeke pi opua iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yeni na hasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ dokeda hali paęž‰taęž‰ na polo pelemepate pa yeni hasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ dokeda hali paęž‰taęž‰ pelimikie leekeme. Tiki tiki hau pu halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la winaęž‰yeke wi loluekemaęž‰ na epoaęž‰me leekeme. Hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la winaęž‰yeke wi loluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Ne wahapaęž‰ pimiki hau paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰14-17, Luku 5ęž‰33-39)
\p 
\v 18 Kutupataęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make Paęž‰tisi haliweki make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone uluekemaęž‰ ne wahapaęž‰ pimikime. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Pa ekipeke mo Dioninaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ make Paęž‰tisi haliwekinaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ make ne wahapaęž‰ piaęž‰tiki pitelemepate pa nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto hau na pu halemepe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\p 
\v 19 Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰ panake mea kiki taęž‰maęž‰ni pitaęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ teke halimaęž‰ wi leeke epemeke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ne na neke pa hapeke na yelieke leekeme.
\v 20 Kutu pimipate nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ teke hali hatuku pelieke. Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ ne wahapaęž‰ pea hatiki pilimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ daunaęž‰ panake dau sinkipiki mea talao na tumbulu halaęž‰me leekeme. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ panake dau sinkipiki talaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ dau sinkipa kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ tieke wilieke leekeme. Ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ sinkipi ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoelieke leekeme.
\v 22 Koto tupaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ panake waini ikali ambaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yonkeleke ipi kanake manunaęž‰ na holo pambo halaęž‰me laa pa holo pambeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ panake waini ikalimaęž‰ dako aęž‰meiyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yonkeleke kanake yambilieke leekeme. Kutupa waini ikali make maęž‰naęž‰ yonkeleke kanakemanu make telipinaęž‰ hoelieke leekeme. Kotoeki na pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo panake waini ikalitaęž‰ panake maęž‰naęž‰ yonkeleke kanake manunaęž‰ holo pambilieke leekeme.
\s1 Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ pi lemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰1-8, Luku 6ęž‰1-5)
\p 
\v 23 Yesutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate homekenaęž‰ mo konimaęž‰ handeke ale widi e manunaęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ widi kilikimanu hondaęž‰ mepi pu mimikime.
\v 24 Kutupataęž‰ Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰e laa Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ piaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰eki pitolo pitelememe. Pa ekipeke pitelemepe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande Deipidimaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na yataęž‰pemepe.
\v 26 Deipidi ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke haliwekitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wieke palaowa naakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yeni peao haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ homeke napeke yeeke palaowa kone naakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke haliweki make mea haleekeme leekeme. Abaiyaęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ you hali hayeke pitaęž‰ pimikime. Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ na yataęž‰pemepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali epeaenaęž‰yeke Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰pate pa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ biki daeyaenaęž‰yeke wepia na paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ Tekehali kone halaęž‰me leekeme.
\c 3
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ kiki hoke hali epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰9-14, Luku 6ęž‰6-11)
\p 
\v 1 Yesutaęž‰ Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ paa hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ kiki hapueke endiki hali homeke koto da paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme.
\v 2 Kutupataęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu handaęž‰ pelia haemekeme. Pa ekipeke Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ kiki epeaaliepe o na epeaaliepe hone wia handaęž‰ pelia hataęž‰ pi yambaęž‰leaęž‰me loluekemaęž‰ handaęž‰ pelia haemekeme.
\v 3 Koto pimipate Yesumaęž‰ kiki hapueke endiki hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do paęž‰taęž‰ epoe leekeme.
\v 4 Epeeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ aleke wape pea ulaęž‰pe leekeme. Wandaęž‰hali epeaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe o hoeyaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe laa ombu alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali mea tiaowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe o homaoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe leekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰ pi na leke pa pambo haemekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ mo haliweki handolo hataęž‰ lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ pea handeekeme. Ikaęž‰ hone takaęž‰laeyeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kiki tindipae leekeme. Koto leeke handaa ipikaęž‰ kiki tindipaeyeke epeekeme.
\v 6 Koto kone mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ hama opolu baotaęž‰ Hetodinaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ Yesu luekemaęž‰ tome tome pambemekeme.
\s1 Yeni haemeke wandaęž‰hali Yesumaęž‰ mea tiaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Kaęž‰lili ikali leke paęž‰taęž‰ pemeketaęž‰ tapake tieke teliekeme. Kaęž‰lili wandaęž‰hali Diudia wandaęž‰hali
\v 8 Diutuseleme wandaęž‰hali make Idumia kenke nane haemeke wandaęž‰hali make Diodani ikali nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane haemeke wandaęž‰hali make Taiya Saidoni yaapo nane haemeke wandaęž‰hali make paeyaomaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pieke ekimanu paeyao opimiki handaataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 9 Kutupataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wandaęž‰hali wopu yaęž‰leke IĚ± pendila pendila peaamaęž‰naęž‰ kawaso homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea aęž‰pa endi baape leekeme.
\v 10 Pa ekipeke Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu epeaeyeke handaataęž‰ mo yeni pambemeke wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Yesu wataaluekemaęž‰ pasaęž‰tei pimikime.
\v 11 Kutupataęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitieke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu handolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰punialo ende pitolo hataęž‰ hoke eĚ± wi laęž‰ paleke paleke pitolo hataęž‰ dupa lemekeme. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekee lemekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ hando alo alotaęž‰ IĚ± na peneme yaapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki 12 miekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰1-4, Luku 6ęž‰12-16)
\p 
\v 13 Kutupataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pote maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰meiya puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone pieke haliweki wi laęž‰ mepi pieketaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 14-15 Yesumaęž‰ 12 haliweki ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± hao haenaęž‰yeke haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ pi walo puaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰yeke ipikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki halolo alotaęž‰ Hoke temokomanu tolu luemenaęž‰yeke kitolome leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki tapa tapa puluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ hataęž‰ leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Mo haliwekinaęž‰ biki manutaęž‰ Saimono biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke bikitaęž‰ Pida leekeme.
\v 17 Diaęž‰mesi Dioni hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰taęž‰ Sepedinaęž‰ eiyeke yaapo Yesumaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ biki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Boanaęž‰si leekeme. Do bikitaęž‰ Tutu litaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ eiyekee.
\v 18-19 Aęž‰ndutu Pilipi Badolomiu make Maęž‰tiu make Tomasi make Aęž‰lopiaęž‰sinaęž‰ eiyeke Diaęž‰mesi make Taęž‰diaęž‰si make Saimono Seloti make mo Isekatioti hali Diudasitaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰ polo pieke hali make do haliweki paeyaonaęž‰ bikimanue.
\p 
\v 20 Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ da peekeme. Wandaęž‰hali wopu pa mombelemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ne napeke nate diaęž‰yekeme.
\v 21 Doeki opuaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake titimaęž‰ Yesu handaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ pemekeme. Pa ekipeke mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone momataęž‰laęž‰me leaęž‰tiki pimikieki opuaataęž‰ pemekeme.
\s1 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰22-32, Luku 11ęž‰14-23, 12ęž‰10)
\p 
\v 22 Mandane wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Diutuseleme da nane hao aęž‰pa Yesu hayeke alenaęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Bielisibulumaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ talolo paęž‰laęž‰me laa Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke temoko manunaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu linaęž‰ piaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa alotaęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ ipiki kone ekipa teliepe leekeme.
\v 24 Mo kenke homekenaęž‰ Kapomanimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone putupa alu alu pea aęž‰ndaęž‰ liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hapeke na yelieke leekeme.
\v 25 Homeke tapake wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone putupa alu alu pea aęž‰ndaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto tapaketaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hapeke na yelieke leekeme.
\v 26 Kutupataęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ ipiki kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ lia hone yaapo wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ hapeke na yelieke. Ipikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paelieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 27 Kutu piliepate maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo honkopu halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ pake muluekemaęž‰ pa pondaęž‰pe lia puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Titinaęž‰taęž‰ mo honkopu halaęž‰ hali ambaęž‰la tonkao ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ mea puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 28-29 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hoke hau peleme ekimanu paeyao make ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki lo hoeyaaseme ekimanu make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ biki lo hoeyaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paeya wahapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Koto hoke hautaęž‰ hoto paeyao pa u halieke leekeme.
\v 30 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hoke temoko talolo paęž‰laęž‰me laa lemeke handaataęž‰ koto pimanu Yesumaęž‰ leekeme.
\s1 Yesu ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰hali
\r (Maęž‰tiu 12ęž‰46-50, Luku 8ęž‰19-21)
\p 
\v 31 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke titimaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane hataęž‰ Yesu epenaęž‰ pi laęž‰niaemekeme.
\v 32 Yesutaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mombaęž‰la pitimiki ale tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ kame titimaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane hataęž‰ neke epoelenaęž‰ handeteke halememe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 33-34 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya amaęž‰ ya kametiti epipe laataęž‰ mo mombaęž‰la pitimiki wandaęž‰hali handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ ya amaęž‰ ya kametiti do pilimime laa
\v 35 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ ya kame ya anaęž‰ ya amaęž‰ halememe leekeme.
\c 4
\s1 Wae ale manunaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰1-9, Luku 8ęž‰4-8)
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande ikali leke teaęž‰naęž‰ hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pi pa waleekeme. Wandaęž‰hali wopu aęž‰pa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mombelemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ haenaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ wieke palai kawaso homekenaęž‰ pua pitiekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa pimanu wotu waleekeme. Pi walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\p 
\v 3 Opuaęž‰pe. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wae alemanu tandeloluekemaęž‰ peekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa tandelaęž‰tiki pulu haenaęž‰ mandane wae manutaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ lopaęž‰ lopaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ ba titimaęž‰ aęž‰pa talopu nemekeme laataęž‰
\v 5 Mandane wae manutaęž‰ toopimanu manda taleeke kenke sikinaęž‰ lopeekeme. Koto wae sunu koto kone opeekepate kenke hosiki siki taleekeeki yaalo hataęž‰
\v 6 nate talo hataęž‰ piki lopaapeke na yaalo pou ta hapiekeme
\v 7 Mandane wae manutaęž‰ tekeke hake ale polu paęž‰taęž‰manu lopeekeme. Kutupa mo tekeke hake alemanu opaęž‰liaaso hande wae alemanu opolo pieke ekitaęž‰ tumbuaeyekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰ kiliki na aęž‰eyekeme.
\v 8 Kutu piekepate mandane wae ale manutaęž‰ epeke kenkenaęž‰ lopeekeeki patela opaęž‰liaotaęž‰ napeke wiekeeki manutaęž‰ dupae. Mandaneeki 30 tupaęž‰ mandaneeki 60 tupaęž‰ mandaneeki 100 tupaęž‰ wiekeme leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Katake lombaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ wotu opinaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Pi manutaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰maęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ teke
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰10-17, Luku 8ęž‰9-10)
\p 
\v 10 Ipikaęž‰ honu make haenaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali pemeke nanetaęž‰ ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hande 12 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 11 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki aęž‰mbaalaęž‰ ekimanu handilimikie. Pate pa hao haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekimanu homeke opilimikie.
\q1 
\v 12 Handenaęž‰yeke onkolumaęž‰manu laęž‰laęž‰pate handaęž‰ winaęž‰yeke na laęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 Opinaęž‰yeke onkolumaęž‰ pimanu laęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ hone winaęž‰yeke na laęž‰laęž‰me.
\q1 Opimikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaalo piaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Wae tandelaasaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teke la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰18-23, Luku 8ęž‰11-15)
\p 
\v 13 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do onkolumaęž‰ alo ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na witelemepe. Kotaęž‰ do alo ekitaęž‰ hone na wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ aloeki paeyao ekipa hone wilimikipe leekeme.
\v 14 Hande wae alemanu tandeleeke halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi alemanu tandelo halaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 15 Mo hande potaęž‰naęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi alemanu lopaęž‰ lopaęž‰ pu halaęž‰me. Kutupa opitolo haenaęž‰ kone mo tandeleeke pi ale manutaęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ koto kone aęž‰pa yokaęž‰ mea pu halaęž‰me.
\v 16-17 Mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ toopi manda taleeke kenke sikinaęž‰ lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰ wae ale manumaęž‰ handelememe. Pi opuelemepate koto kone taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ minelemepate wopu na mendiaake hosiki hao kutupa kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰eki make koto pi alenaęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto kone lopo halememe leekeme.
\v 18 Mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo tekeke hapeleke ale polu paęž‰taęž‰ tandeleeke wae ale manumaęž‰ handelememe leekeme. Mo hande pi alemanu opitelemepate
\v 19 kenke hau hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ hamoko alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ mandane alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ we pambaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ mo hande pi alemanu daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniki pitaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ napeke na u halememe leekeme.
\v 20 Kutu pitelemepate mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ epeke kenke seliaponaęž‰ lopeekeeki manumaęž‰ handelememe laa pi alemanu opua meataęž‰ kutupa napeke aęž‰eyo halememe leekeme. Mandaneeki 30 tupaęž‰ mandaneeki 60 tupaęž‰ mandaneeki 100 tupaęž‰ aęž‰eyo halememe leekeme.
\s1 PaĚ±aĚ± aęž‰mbaasaęž‰ pi
\r (Luku 8ęž‰16-18)
\p 
\v 21 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Olaęž‰pake mea epemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ disi tieke oto paęž‰taęž‰ wilimikipe o bedi tokele paęž‰taęž‰ wilimikipe. Diaęž‰me. Manda keo u halememe leekeme.
\v 22 Kutupa pankaęž‰ wilimieki manutaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ walenaęž‰yeke pankaęž‰ wilimime. Aęž‰mbao wilimieki manutaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰penaęž‰yeke aęž‰mbao wilimime leekeme.
\v 23 Katake lombaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ wotu opinaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo opiteleme ekimanu hone wopu wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ haleme tupaęž‰ kone koto anaęž‰naęž‰ paa milimikie. Kutupa pa hakaęž‰taęž‰pao mandane ekimanu make milimikie leekeme.
\v 25 Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wia halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ mandane ekimanu make hakaęž‰taęž‰pao milieke leekeme. Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na wia halaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na milieke. Ipikaęž‰ wia halaęž‰eki kone mataęž‰lieke leekeme.
\s1 Wae ale ipiki kone opaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 26 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki dupae. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wae alemanu kenkenaęž‰ tandeleekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa timbaęž‰ leeke peliaęž‰tiki da kaęž‰laęž‰peeke tiatiki piekeme. Kutupa hande wae alemanu patela opaęž‰liaeyekeme. Opaęž‰liao pieke ekitaęž‰ ekipa opaęž‰laęž‰pe mo halitaęž‰ mateekeme.
\v 28 Wae ale manutaęž‰ kenkemaęž‰ peaaseke handaa wae ale opo halememe. Katake titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰laęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paataęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ honke pankaataęž‰ kutupa napeke panka tumbaęž‰ wilieke leekeme.
\v 29 Kutu piliepate napeke naa piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto kone kepetemaęž‰ pokaęž‰mepi pilieke. Mo naa pitaęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰ yaęž‰leke handaa milieke leekeme.
\s1 Masidadi waenaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰31-32,34, Luku 13ęž‰18-19)
\p 
\v 30 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ alekemaęž‰ handenaęž‰ lolumaęž‰pe o eki onkolumaęž‰ lolumaęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 31 Ipikitaęž‰ masidadi wae ale sikimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme. Mo wae alesiki otaęž‰ hosiki alesiki yaęž‰laęž‰pate
\v 32 kenkenaęž‰ nokepeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ opaęž‰liaotaęž‰ beli pondaęž‰pa otaęž‰ tieke halieke laa kutupa paleke paleke tiekemanu piliaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kototaęž‰ ba titimaęž‰ katake tuĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa dake hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Kutupiki onkolumaęž‰manu Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleeke ekitaęž‰ opuma homaenaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 34 Onkolumaęž‰manu pi waleekepate pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na waleke ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke pi tekemanu la haleekeme.
\s1 Yesunaęž‰ pimaęž‰ po tilipu make ikali homanu make tunkulaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰23-27, Luku 8ęž‰22-25)
\p 
\v 35 Koto onkolumaęž‰ leeke natenaęž‰ welealo nane Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ do ikali tunkula mo teaęž‰ nane pomanaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 36 Kutupa wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao Yesutaęž‰ mo kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ pitieke tupaęž‰ pitaęž‰ pelia haenaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ mea pemekeme. Kawaso mandane ekimanu make tonkaęž‰naęž‰ apaęž‰tao pemekeme.
\v 37 Po tilipu tieke epeekeme. Kutupa ikali ho aęž‰meiya mo kawaso litolo hataęž‰ ikali pambo tumbiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo kawasonaęž‰ ikalimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ tumbuluekemaęž‰ dodo piekeme.
\v 38 Kutu piekepate Yesutaęž‰ kawaso mendeke nane pita kaęž‰ndaęž‰ lia peliekeme. Haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu mea tiao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Niki homolumaęž‰maęž‰ hone na witelepe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Yesumaęž‰ tiao mo po tilipu paęž‰taęž‰ make mo ikali paęž‰taęž‰ make pi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pae. Tunkulie leekeme. Po tilipu tunkula ikali laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ na piki pa wiekeme.
\v 40 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Alekenaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homelemepe. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone na tulaasemepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 41 Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi lemekeeki dupa. Do halitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Po tilipumaęž‰ make ikalimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ pi opua tunkuliaęž‰me lemekeme.
\c 5
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ hoke temokomaęž‰ keao hayeke hali homeke epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 8ęž‰28-34, Luku 8ęž‰26-39)
\p 
\v 1 Mo hande ikali leke mone teaęž‰ nane yopuataęž‰ mo Kedasa wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kenke nane pemekeme.
\v 2-3 Kutupa koto kone mo kawaso minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaataęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitieke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ mandaęž‰ hande piekeme. Mo halitaęž‰ hali holiki u hayeke tikene da paęž‰taęž‰manu hao opolo aęž‰pa Yesu mandaęž‰ hande pipikime. Hande halitaęž‰ koto tikenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu hao hayekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ seni pumaęž‰ kone ipiki pa tonkaapeke na yeekeme.
\v 4 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ hoto eleke eleke ipikaęž‰ kiki anke yaapo seni pu manumaęž‰ tonkao haemekepate ipikaęž‰ kiki tonkao hayeke seni pumanu tunkulaęž‰tiki piekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ anke tonkao hayeke seni pumanu tunkulu bepi piaęž‰tiki piekeme. Kutupataęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu hao homu peaapeke na yeekeme.
\v 5 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tikene da paęž‰taęž‰manu pote paęž‰taęž‰manu make timba natenaęž‰ hoto paeyao eĚ± wi alo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone toopimaęž‰ litolo hataęž‰ hao hayekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ papate hataęž‰ Yesu hando haotaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya pua ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaeyekeme.
\v 7 Kutupa pi anekehapu alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesuo. Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ oli Manda Halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ Tiekenaęž‰ Eiyekee leekeme. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ eki puluekemaęž‰ aęž‰pa pipe laa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± handolo haenaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alo IĚ± tanda tanda na peaapee leekeme.
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Hoke temokoo. Do hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao pue leeke handaa mo halimaęž‰ koto leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka bikitaęž‰ Eleke elekee laataęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ wopu eleke eleke halomeke handa loaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 10 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ Mo hoke temokomanu do kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao na penaęž‰ laa honke honke wopu leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Maęž‰naęž‰ titi peiyene teaęž‰naęž‰ ne nalo haenaęž‰
\v 12 mo hoke temoko manumaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ honke lemekeeki dupa. Maęž‰naęž‰ titinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu pomono lae lemekeme.
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ pitulu penaęž‰ leekeme. Mo hoke temoko manumaęž‰ mo hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao maęž‰naęž‰ titinaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitulu pemekeme. Koto maęž‰naęž‰ tititaęž‰ 2 daoseni tupaęž‰ mo peiyene sesemeĚ±leĚ±naęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya holaęž‰paęž‰niao ikali paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ ikali naa honki lemekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰titi handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ pindipa puaataęž‰ daoni nane haemeke wandaęž‰hali topu da paęž‰taęž‰manu haemeke wandaęž‰hali make laęž‰tiki pomimikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hande pieke ekimanu handuluekemaęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande weleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temokomanu pitieke hali koto paęž‰taęž‰ dau yama epeke hone wia pitiekeeki handemeke handaa paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa ambaęž‰ hande hoke temokomanu pitieke hali paęž‰taęž‰ pieke ekimanu make mo maęž‰naęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ pieke ekimanu make handemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ la hale hale pimikime.
\p 
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto kone Yesu ikaęž‰ kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao penaęž‰yeke Pu pu lemekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Hande kawasonaęž‰ kone pitulu pulu haenaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hoke temokomanu pitieke halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ Hapanaęž‰e laa pi wopu leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ na epenaęž‰ laakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ peaasaęž‰ ekimanu make neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make nakaęž‰ yankeketiti paęž‰taęž‰ pua lapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Mo halimaęž‰ Daoni kiki yaapo haemeke kenke nane puaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ ekimanu waloendi piekeme. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\s1 Diaitusinaęž‰ waneke pitaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ dau wataeyeke wandaęž‰ yaapo
\r (Maęž‰tiu 9ęž‰18-26, Luku 8ęž‰40-56)
\p 
\v 21 Yesu mo kawasonaęž‰ pita mone teaęž‰naęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la peeketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mombelemekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ tunkulu pa ulaęž‰ ikali teaęž‰naęž‰ haenaęž‰ mombelemekeme.
\v 22 Pi hotu haemeke da you hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Diaitisimaęž‰ aęž‰pa Yesunaęž‰ anke teke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao honke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 23 Ya wandikisiki otaęž‰ homuluekemaęž‰ taapolo pilaęž‰me leekeme. Tiao haenaęž‰yeke nakanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰pa nakaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ ipiki wataapeke leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Kutupa Yesu Diaitusi yaapo pepekeme. Wandaęž‰hali wopu Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± pulu hataęž‰ pendila pendila putia pemekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayekeme. Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ bapi 12 tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ we yopu hayekeme.
\v 26 Dokeda titimaęž‰ taapemeke ekimaęž‰ tanda halo haemekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mani paeyao pa batiki piekepate we na tunkuliki pa daeyatiki piekeme.
\v 27 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lemeke pi mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ opuaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ pua Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau wataeyekeme.
\v 28 Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ dau wataokaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± epeaalieke hone wiekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Kutupa koto kone we yopu hayekeeki tunkula ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ hande yeni paeyaęž‰me. Ametaęž‰ tiaasome hone wiekeme.
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone hone witolo hataęž‰ ya wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki mandane ekitaęž‰ peaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone wiekeme. Kutupa koto kone mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epinaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ ya dau wataeyaęž‰pe leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰taa. Do wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ pendila pendila piteleme ekitaęž‰ do handolo hataęž‰ kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epimaęž‰ wataeyaęž‰pe aleme lemekepate
\p 
\v 32 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki wataeyeke wandaęž‰ o hali handuluekemaęž‰ hando hopaęž‰liaeyekeme.
\v 33 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki epeaeyekeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ putu putu lutiki aęž‰pa Yesunaęž‰ anke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰puniaeyekeme. Kutupa Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ekimanu pi peneme yao laataęž‰ hande alemanu la haleekeme.
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya wandikio. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaase ekimaęž‰ tiaaseme. Puki lopaniao puaęž‰peke. Nakaęž‰ yeni paeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 35 Yesumaęž‰ pi pa alo haenaęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ hande pi hotu haemeke da you halinaęž‰ da nane hao aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ wandikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeaęž‰me laa Ekipeke mo Disa honke loloendi pitelepe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 36 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ na opiki mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pa hone tulaapeke leekeme.
\v 37 Yesumaęž‰ Pida pitaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi Dioni hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ make koto haliweki homeke ipiki telinaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 38 Pi hotu haemeke da you halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekepate Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ eĚ± la alu alu pitolo haemekeeki opiekeme.
\v 39 Kutupa hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipeke eĚ± la alu alu pitelemepe. Mo wandikitaęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰pate uĚ± pelaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 40 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ki taemekeme. Kutu pimikipate Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao hama tolu liekeme. Wandikinaęž‰ inkiki ateke yaapo ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± haemeke haliweki make wandiki wieke alenaęž‰ hatuku peekeme.
\v 41 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandikinaęž‰ kiki minaakaęž‰naęž‰ alotaęž‰ Talida kumi o Wandikio. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ tiae alome leekeme.
\p 
\v 42 Kuta kone mo wandiki tiao potaęž‰ pomiekeme. Ipikaęž‰ bapitaęž‰ 12 paeyeke handaa loaęž‰me. Koto piekeeki handaataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua pomomaęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 43 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke leekeme. Kutupa wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ ne mea halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\c 6
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete da nane peekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 13ęž‰53-58, Luku 4ęž‰16-30)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± da nane pemekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa mo Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ Diu haliwekinaęž‰ pi hotu haemeke da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba puaataęž‰ pi waleekeme. Mo yeni pu haemeke da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimiki wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ opua penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do walaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyaotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰ opua paęž‰laęž‰pe. Do halimaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke honemanu ekipa handaęž‰ wia mea paęž‰laęž‰pe laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu do aleke welemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 3 Do halitaęž‰ kapenda hali diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa Metinaęž‰ eiyeke diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Diaęž‰mesi Diosepe Diudasi make Saimono make ipikaęž‰ hameke titi diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe laa Ipikaęž‰ beliki titi do paęž‰taęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± na halemepe lemekeme. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pitolo hataęž‰ lemekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Koto lemeke ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ potopede halitaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opu halemepate ipikaęž‰ da haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ tapake manumaęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi na opilimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu piaęž‰peke na yeekepate pa yeni hayeke wandaęž‰halimanu ipikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ minaa ikaęž‰ yeni tandelaeyekeme.
\v 6 Ikaęž‰ hone na tulaemeke ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pominolo hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ekipeke pi na opitolo pitelemepe hone wiekeme. Kutupa mo da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu pominolo hataęž‰ pi walaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki tapaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 10ęž‰5-15, Luku 9ęž‰1-6)
\p 
\v 7 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo hande 12 haliweki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰yeke wi laęž‰ mea yaapo la la pu tapa tapa piekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu tolu linaęž‰yeke ipikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki haleekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa manaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tumapu homeke mea minaa alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na mea miniki puaęž‰paęž‰peke laataęž‰ tia nu make mani make na mea puaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 9 Anke dake pambaotaęž‰ sedi yaapo atulao na pambaake puaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 10 Pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ make alotaęž‰ Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pelia haluekemaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hao hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa mo damanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao da maęž‰ndaęž‰ halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pua haeme dataęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 11 Da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki na handaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi na opimiki kiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ na hake pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ talaęž‰laęž‰ dokolo tandelapaęž‰peke. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kiaemekeeki tombo waluekemaęž‰ tandelapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Kutupa mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ puaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la wiaęž‰paęž‰peke laataęž‰
\v 13 hoke temokomanu wopu tolu liaataęž‰ yeni haemeke wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ younaęž‰ honkumaęž‰ handeke ale lekeeki holaotaęž‰ tandelenaęž‰ peaemekeme.
\s1 Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionitaęž‰ homeekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰1-12, Luku 9ęž‰7-9)
\p 
\v 14 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ biki kende tupaęž‰ winaęž‰ lemeke handaa Kini Hetodimaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ tapaeyeke haliwekimaęž‰ pieke ekimanu opiekeme. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionitaęž‰ homa kone paa tiao piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ do wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu pitolo piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto lemekepate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ Elaidia yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekepate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa ambaęž‰ kone hayeke hali tupaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Hetodimaęž‰ koto pimanu opua alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ Dionie. IĚ±maęž‰ you tunkuluaęž‰ hali tiao piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\v 17 Ambaęž‰taęž‰ Hetodimaęž‰ Dioni yolaęž‰ mea epenaęž‰yeke haliweki tapaotaęž‰ Dionitaęž‰ tonkao dipula mea lopaeyekeme. Hetodiasimaęž‰ honke leeke handaa piekeme. Hetodiasitaęž‰ Hetodinaęž‰ hameke Pilipinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ hayekepate Hetodimaęž‰ petolo miekeme.
\v 18 Dionimaęž‰ Hetodi paęž‰taęž‰ pi ambaęž‰ leekeeki dupa. Nakaęž‰ kamenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ petolo mele ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Koto leeke handaataęž‰ Hetodiasimaęž‰ Dioni paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ luekemaęž‰ hoĚ±lindaęž‰lu hayekepate liaęž‰peke na yekeme.
\v 20 Hetodimaęž‰taęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ tiki tiki hau pu hayekeeki make yako piki hali make handeeke handaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ panka mea hao hayekeme. Dionimaęž‰ walaęž‰tiki pieke pimanu Hetodimaęž‰ opua weiyaęž‰tiki piekepate taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa opuaęž‰tiki piekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Hetodimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mendieke nate epeeke handaataęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kapomani tumiki haliweki make ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tumiki haliweki make Kaęž‰lili nane haemeke hali tieke tieke make wi laęž‰ mepi pieke aęž‰pa mombelemekeme. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Hetodiasimaęž‰ Yaka natee hone wiekeme.
\v 22 Hetodiasinaęž‰ wanekemaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ keliapo pambolo hataęž‰ Hetodi make epemeke haliweki make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaeyeke handaa kini halimaęž‰ mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ale IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ kulueke leekeme.
\v 23 Mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ale IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ honke lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ kulueke. Ya kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki kone putupa otaęž‰ kulueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Koto leeke handaa mo wandikimaęž‰ puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pea alotaęž‰ Aleke honke lonope leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰ hali Dioni ipikaęž‰ you honke lae leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Kutupa mo wandikimaęž‰ koto kone kini hali paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± aęž‰pa honke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ aletaęž‰ mo bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰ hali Dioninaęž‰ youtaęž‰ metekinaęž‰ wia ame do kone kuelenaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Mo kini halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ tanda wotu homeekepate mo laęž‰ wieke pimanu leeke handaa make mo epemeke haliweki haemeke handaa make ipikaęž‰ pi tunkulaęž‰peke na yeeke handaataęž‰
\v 27 kotaęž‰ koto kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndeli miniki hali homekemaęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ you tunkulu mea epenaęž‰yeke tapaeyekeme. Kutupa mo halimaęž‰ puaataęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ Dioninaęž‰ you tunkula
\v 28 metekinaęž‰ wia mea aęž‰paataęž‰ mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme. Mo wandikimaęž‰ meataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ inkiki paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 29 Dioninaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki manumaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ toko mulu puaataęž‰ toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua tu wimikime.
\s1 Pi mea pemeke haliwekitaęž‰ paa epemekeeki
\r (Luku 9ęž‰10)
\p 
\v 30 Hande tapaeyeke haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ paa aęž‰paataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi walemeke ekimanu make ikaęž‰ pimiki ekimanu paeyao make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lemekeme.
\v 31 Wandaęž‰hali wopu pa aęž‰paęž‰tiki puaęž‰tiki pimiki handaa Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ne napeke nate diaęž‰ yeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki homeke pomanaęž‰ ipupe. Mo Keneme nane hoto siki pitulu pomanaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 32 Kutupa ambaęž‰ hande kawasonaęž‰ pita keneme nane pemekeme.
\p 
\v 33 Keneme nane pemekepate wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pemekeeki handolo hataęž‰ dotaęž‰ handaęž‰ haliweki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone wimikime. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ daoni paeyao minaęž‰paęž‰lao anke hao pakaęž‰lao puaataęž‰ Yesu ameda aĚ±iĚ± na opolo yapemeke haenaęž‰ iki ambaęž‰la opolo yapemekeme.
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ mo kawaso minaęž‰paęž‰lao kenke nane opolo pulu hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu handaataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo handeteke halaęž‰ hali diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu tupaęž‰ handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ eĚ± alo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme. Kutupa pimanu wopu waleekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ 5 daoseni haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ne haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰13-21, Luku 9ęž‰10-17, Dioni 6ęž‰1-14)
\p 
\v 35 Kutupa nate paetaęž‰leke handaa ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Do anetaęž‰ keneme nanee. Ametaęž‰ nate paetaęž‰laęž‰me laa
\v 36 topu da aneke da paęž‰taęž‰manu make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ne hambaęž‰tiki penaęž‰ tapa tapa pie lemekeme.
\p 
\v 37 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nemanu mandaneeki mea halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ 200 kina mea pua palaowa hambaataęž‰ iki nenaęž‰yeke halomono alepe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 38 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo palaowa kitiki siki ekipu halemepe handolo pupe leekeme. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaa paa aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Yunki hataęž‰ ulaęž‰me kutupa taęž‰pelitaęž‰ yaapo ulaęž‰me lemekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Koto lemeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo nomaęž‰ seliaponaęž‰ mombaęž‰la pitumaęž‰ pitumaęž‰ pea pitaęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 40 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande mombaęž‰la pitumaęž‰ pitumaęž‰ pemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mandaneeki 100 tupaęž‰ mandaneeki 50 tupaęž‰ pitumaęž‰ pitumaęž‰ pea pitimikime.
\v 41 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ hande palaowa kitiki siki yunki hataęž‰ make hande taęž‰peli yaapo make minaataęž‰ ya nane handaęž‰liao Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae laataęž‰ palaowa kitiki sunu pindi pindi pea ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mea wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰yeke hale hale piekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰peli yaapo make pindi pindi pea disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ hale hale pinaęž‰ haleekeme.
\v 42 Paeyaomaęž‰ naakaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Weleke talaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 43 Mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pa wieke palaowa taęž‰peli putu piliki pa wieke ekimanu meataęž‰ nu 12 tumbaemekeme.
\v 44 Kutupa hande palaowa kitiki sunu nemeke haliwekitaęž‰ 5 daoseni haliwekie.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ ikali manda peekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰22-33, Dioni 6ęž‰15-21)
\p 
\v 45 Koto kone Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kawasonaęž‰ pita mone teaęž‰naęž‰ halaęž‰ da Betesaida da paęž‰taęž‰ iki ambaęž‰la opolo puaęž‰paęž‰peke laataęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰hali wopu tapa tapa piekeme.
\v 46 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ pote paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pulu peekeme.
\v 47 Timbaęž‰leke hautaęž‰ kawaso ikali tukikinaęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honu makesiki kenkenaęž‰ hayekeme.
\v 48 Yesumaęž‰ handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ deli awolo hataęž‰ po tieke wenoko nane epeeke handaa weleke we pimikieki handeekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰puluekemaęž‰ okonaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo haliweki haemeke alenaęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ ikali manda ankenaęž‰ peekeme. Lombei pu pa poluekemaęž‰ hone wiekepate
\v 49 mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki ikali manda ankenaęž‰ peekeeki handaataęž‰ temokopate ipulaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ eĚ± wi lemekeme.
\v 50 Paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki handolo hataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ wotu homemekeme.
\p Kutu pimikipate koto kone Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Honkopu hape. Dotaęž‰ IĚ±e. Paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰pepee leekeme.
\v 51 Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ mo kawasonaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pitulu peeke haenaęž‰taęž‰ po tieke tunkuliekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime.
\v 52 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande 5 daoseni wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ palaowa kitiki sunu telipieke ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ hone lenkipa na wimiki ekiyalo hone na wimikime.
\s1 Kenesatete paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 14ęž‰34-36)
\p 
\v 53 Mo kawasonaęž‰ ikali tunkula puaataęž‰ Kenesatete nane opolo puaataęž‰ mo kawaso aęž‰ndimikime.
\v 54 Kawaso minaęž‰paęž‰laemeketaęž‰ kutaa kone wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke handolo hataęž‰ hone wimikime.
\v 55 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto da ninaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya pua mo yeni hapa wieke wandaęž‰hali tilinaęž‰ mu wiaataęž‰ Yesu hayeke paęž‰taęž‰ mea pemekeme.
\v 56 Yesu peeke alenaęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ da nane make daonimanu make topu topu da ninaęž‰ make opolo peeke dinaęž‰ da nane yeni hapa wimiki wandaęž‰hali mea tia pua makedi yalao tu umaęž‰ umaęž‰ pimikime. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ dau honiki wataaluekemaęž‰ honke lemekeme. Wataemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni tandelemekeme.
\c 7
\s1 Apaęž‰meinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu
\r (Maęž‰tiu 15ęž‰1-9)
\p 
\v 1 Paęž‰tisi haliweki make mandane wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliweki make Diutuseleme da minaęž‰paęž‰lao aęž‰paataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mombelemekeme.
\v 2 Kutupa Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ na tandepemeke kikimaęž‰ ne nemekeeki handemekeme. Mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ dupiki tandepeaęž‰peke laa lemeke tupaęž‰ kiki na tandepemekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Hande Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ make Diu haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make apaęž‰meinaęž‰ haumanu pu haemekeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ ne noluekemaęž‰ kiki ambaęž‰la tandepo haemekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa makedinaęž‰ hao aęž‰paataęž‰ ikali aĚ±iĚ± na peki hataęž‰taęž‰ ne aĚ±iĚ± na netiki pu halememe. Ikaęž‰ apaęž‰meinaęž‰ titinaęž‰ haumanu make wopu opua pu halememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ kapomanu make sosepenimanu make kopamaęž‰ wepiki metekimanu make bedi make tandepo halememe.
\p 
\v 5 Kutupa mo Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ateke meiyekenaęž‰ haumanu na opiki ekipeke kiki hoke ekimaęž‰ ne no halemepe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ yayapiki hau pu haleme haliwekie laataęž‰ Aisayamaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ wape piekeeki dupa.
\q1 Do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hambilikimaęž‰ yaka biki mea aęž‰meiyaasemepate ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ hone taęž‰taęž‰ witelememe.
\q1 
\v 7 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke pandaęž‰ puniao yeni pu halememe. Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi wieke ekimanue alo hataęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ ateke meiyekenaęž‰ wimikieki kone walo halememe laa
\q1 wape piekeme laataęž‰
\p 
\v 8 Yesumaęž‰ ombu alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu na waleke ikaęž‰ ateke meiyekenaęž‰eki kone walo halememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ateke meiyekenaęž‰ hau pimiki ekimanu pu haleme ekitaęž‰ epeke hau pitolo pimipe laataęž‰
\v 10 Mosesimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ apaęž‰ yaapo oto paęž‰taęž‰ hapeke laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi alaęž‰ halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ liaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 11 Koto leekepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ kulu polo alaęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ Kobana ulaęž‰me leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kobana laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ekie
\v 12 kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ koto alaęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me lo halememe.
\v 13 Do tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ateke meiyekemaęž‰ pimiki ekimanu opitolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ alupaasememe. Kutupa ikaęž‰ hoki nane telieleme haliweki make walo halememe laataęž‰ Koto tupaęž‰ kone mandane haumanu make pu halememe leekeme.
\s1 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ puki haĚ±iĚ± peaasaęž‰ ekimanu
\r (Maęž‰tiu 15ęž‰10-20)
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰yeke paa wi lemipi piekeme. Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paeyao ya pi opua hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 15 Wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hamaęž‰ nane ulaęž‰ alemanu mea nalomaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ na hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰pate tukiki nane wia ipulaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰hali hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 17 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambeeketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 18 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kototaęž‰ iki make pi teke hone na witelemepe leekeme. Yonkeleke hamaęž‰ nane ulaęž‰ alemanu mea nalomaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ tukiki nane peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoeyaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekitaęž‰ hone na witelemepe.
\v 19 Ekipeke. Netaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ na peke ipikaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ hoke ale yapilieke leekeme. Koto pi leeke handaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ nemanu paeyaotaęž‰ pa napeke anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ wia ipulaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hoeyao halememe leekeme.
\v 21 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ puki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ wia hone paęž‰taęž‰ ipu halaęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ dupae. Hoke honemanu make loke apaęž‰taasaęž‰ hau make pake nalaęž‰ hau make hali homenaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰eki make
\v 22 tooli kaęž‰taasaęž‰ hau make we pambaęž‰laęž‰ hau make hoke hoke hau make yayapiki hau make pambaęž‰ na piki hau make ne tunkulaęž‰laęž‰ hau make pi lala pu handaenaęž‰ hau make hone na wiki hau make
\v 23 do haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ pita ipulu hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hoeyao halememe leekeme.
\s1 Wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 15ęž‰21-28)
\p 
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ koto alenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao Taiya nane peekeme. Mo da homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki handaamaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰mbao panka pituluekemaęž‰ peekepate aęž‰mbaapeke na yeekeme.
\v 25 Koto kone wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pieke haumanu opuaataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa ipikaęž‰ anke paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaeyekeme. Koto wandaęž‰naęž‰ wandikitaęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoke temoko pitieke handaataęž‰ piekeme.
\v 26 Ipikitaęž‰ Sitia nane halaęž‰ da Pinisia wandaęž‰ kone hayekepate Kitiki pi lo hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ wandikinaęž‰ weleke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitieke hoke temoko Yesumaęž‰ tolu linaęž‰yeke honke leekeme.
\v 27 Honke leekepate Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Weki wandiki sunumaęž‰ ne ambaęž‰la nenaęž‰e leekeme. Wekiwandiki sununaęž‰ netaęž‰ kika sunu paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ na pilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Koto leekepate koto wandaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Otaęž‰ alepate weki wandiki sunumaęž‰ pindipu lopaęž‰ lopaęž‰ piteleme ekimanu tokele paęž‰taęž‰ kika sunumaęž‰ no halememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto pi leeke handaataęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Pue. Hoke temokomaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandiki minaęž‰paęž‰lao opolu bao peaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 30 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ da puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandiki da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ peli hake wiekeeki handeekepate mo hoke temoko ambaęž‰ peekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ katake poko pi na lo pieke hali epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 31 Yesumaęž‰ Taiya nane laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ minaataęž‰ mo Saidoni nane make Daoni kiki yaapo haemeke kenke nane make lombei pupa Kaęž‰lili ikali leke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo peekeme.
\v 32 Koto paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo pi na opu na lo pieke hali homeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ loke wataenaęž‰yeke honke lemekeme.
\v 33 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipiki hosiki mopateleke wandaęž‰hali na hayeke paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea pua ipikaęž‰ kiki maĚ±leke mo halinaęž‰ katake kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pankaataęž‰ kutupa dopi taataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki maĚ±leke yolaęž‰ mea mo halinaęž‰ kekekenaęž‰ makeke mea kitaeyekeme.
\v 34 Kutupa oli ya nane handaęž‰liaaso hataęž‰ pomomaęž‰ homataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epaęž‰daęž‰e leekeme. Koto pitaęž‰ Lombaęž‰e laa leekeme.
\p 
\v 35 Koto kone ipikaęž‰ katake yaapo lumbupa wiaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kekeke tindipao hayeketaęž‰ kutupa pi epeke tupaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 36 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ manaęž‰ honkopu hao alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ do pitoloeki na lapaęž‰peke leekepate kone wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pa honkopu hao laęž‰tia tia pea hande leeke pitaęž‰ kende tupaęž‰ winaęž‰ lemekeme.
\v 37 Koto pitaęž‰laęž‰eki opimiki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu penkilipaęž‰tia pomuaęž‰tiki pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hau paeyao pieke ekinaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ pu halaęž‰me laataęž‰ pi opuaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ opinaęž‰ pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ pi lenaęž‰ lo halaęž‰me laa lemekeme.
\c 8
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali 4 daoseni paęž‰taęž‰ ne haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 15ęž‰32-39)
\p 
\v 1 Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu tayaemeketaęž‰ kutupa napeke ne diaęž‰yekeme. Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰ lemipi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 2 Do wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ya pukimaęž‰ eĚ± alaęž‰me leekeme. Hoto tepo IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± haememe. Kutupa ametaęž‰ napeke ne diaęž‰me.
\v 3 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ da teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ paleke tapa tapa puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ potaęž‰ hopikinaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie. Mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ papatenaęž‰ hao aęž‰pa pelememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ netaęž‰ handopate mea halomanaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 5 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Palaowa siki ekipu wia halemepe laa lotaęž‰ piekeme. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Watake hataęž‰e lemekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali wopu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kenkenaęž‰ pitaęž‰pe leekeme. Kutupa mo palaowa siki watake hataęž‰ meaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laa pindi pindi peaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale pinaęž‰ haleekeme. Kutupa mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mea hale hale pimikime.
\v 7 Taęž‰peli tepo aęž‰ndaęž‰ make wia haemeke handaa Yesumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do taęž‰pelimanu make mea hale hale pipe leekeme.
\v 8-9 Kutupa paeyaomaęž‰ naa weleke haemekeme. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ naa putu piliki wieke ekitaęž‰ meaataęž‰ alaęž‰ta tieke watake hataęž‰ tumbaemekeme. Wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ 4 daoseni tupaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali haemekeme.
\v 10 Yesumaęž‰ iki paeyao tapa tapa peaataęž‰ koto kone ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± kawaso paęž‰taęž‰ pita Daęž‰laęž‰maęž‰nuta da nane pemekeme.
\s1 Wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ handomono pie lemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 16ęž‰1-4)
\p 
\v 11 Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mineke pi laa ipikaęž‰ anke yololo alotaęž‰ Hepeni nane wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ handomono pie lemekeme.
\v 12 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ pomo tieke wotu homolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ame do haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ekipeke wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ weitelemepe leekeme. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ame do haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handilimikie leekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa mo haliweki minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ kawasonaęž‰ pua pita mone teaęž‰naęž‰ peekeme.
\p 
\v 14 Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ palaowa hone yonkaęž‰lao na mea pemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ kawasonaęž‰ palaowa homekesiki wiekeme.
\v 15 Yesumaęž‰ manaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wotu hapaęž‰peke. Paęž‰tisi haliwekinaęž‰ palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰eki make Hetodinaęž‰ palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰eki make wotu handaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone hone wia pipi lemekeme dupa. Nikitaęž‰ palaowa diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 17 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone wimikieki handaa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ne diaęž‰ yaęž‰leketaęž‰ pa ekipeke pipi alemepe. Ikaęž‰ hone na wiki aĚ±iĚ± na handelemepe. Ikaęž‰ honemanu takaęž‰laalemepe leekeme.
\v 18 Ikaęž‰ leke halaęž‰pate na hando halemepe. Ikaęž‰ katake halaęž‰pate na opu halemepe. Na niminaasemepe.
\v 19 Mo hande palaowa siki yunki hataęž‰ 5 daoseni haliwekinaęž‰ pindi pindi peaowaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ putu pilikimaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰ta tieke ekipu tumba mimipe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ 12 lemekeme.
\p 
\v 20 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande palaowa siki watake hataęž‰ mo 4 daoseni wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pindi pindi peaowaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ putu pilikimaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰ta tieke ekipu tumba mimipe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Watake hataęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 21 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ AĚ±iĚ± na handelemepe leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ leke holupiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ leke epeaeyekeeki
\p 
\v 22 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Betesaida da opolo pemekeme. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ leke holupiki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku aęž‰paataęž‰ koto hali wataenaęž‰yeke Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ honke lemekeme.
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ mo hande leke holupiki halinaęž‰ kiki minaataęž‰ da minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo pate leke hatuku peekeme. Hatuku pua ipikaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ dopi taataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapomaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ kiki tapopao lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ handelepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Mo halimaęž‰ handaęž‰liao alotaęž‰ Haliweki handolopate pa ti leke ale pominelememe leekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapomaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ leke yaapo paa wataeyeke mo halimaęž‰ wotu handaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke telipinaęž‰ pa epeekeme. Kutupa alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao epeke tupaęž‰ handeekeme.
\v 26 Yesumaęž‰ mo hali ipikaęž‰ da tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Da teke nane aĚ±iĚ± na puaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Ketisoe leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 16ęž‰13-20, Luku 9ęž‰18-21)
\p 
\v 27 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± mo Sesatia Pilipai nane damanu paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme. Potaęž‰naęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ piekeme dupa. IĚ±taęž‰ epiyaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ eki lo halemepe laa leekeme.
\v 28 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Bapitaisi peao hayeke hali Dionie. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Elaidiae. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Neketaęž‰ potopede hali maęž‰ndaęž‰e lo halememe lemekeme.
\v 29 Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa lotaęž‰ piekeme dupa. Koto lo halemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epi lo halemepe leekeme. Pidamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Ketisoe leekeme.
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ koto aleme pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tanda meataęž‰ homolueke leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 16ęž‰21-28, Luku 9ęž‰22-27)
\p 
\v 31 Yesumaęž‰ panake pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ tanda tanda tieke wotu milieke leekeme. Mo tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make yeni peao haleme you haliwekimaęž‰ make wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make ipiki kiao limikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ homilieke leekeme. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoto tepo wia paa tiaalieke leekeme.
\v 32 Koto leeke ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme waleekeme. Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ Yesu hosiki mopate leke hatuku mea pua ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutupiki pi na lapeke leekepate
\v 33 Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki handaataęž‰ Pida hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sadani neke pue. IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ na hapeke leekeme. Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ulaęž‰ hone tupaęž‰ na wiki pa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ witeleme hone leke wilimee leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Yesumaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ titi yola pemeke wandaęž‰hali make ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰yeke wi lemipi peaataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya hoki nane toluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone hone ulaęž‰ ekimanu tunkulaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki ti mea tia ya hoki nane telinaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 35 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki miniki hao haluekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki kone alupilieke leekeme. Kutu piliepate IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make do handaęž‰ Pi Seliapo paęž‰taęž‰ make hone witolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki alupaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ otaęž‰ daęž‰taa halieke leekeme.
\v 36 Hali epimaęž‰ do kenke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao ipikaęž‰eki winaęž‰ laa alo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki alupiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epeke ekitaęž‰ ekipa miliepe leekeme.
\v 37 Koto somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki paa muluekemaęž‰ alekemaęž‰ topo peaaliaęž‰pe.
\v 38 Do hande Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone na wiki ti teke yoko haleme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ yaka pi alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ hunkupumaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyekemaęž‰ hunkupumaęž‰ homilieke. Ipikaęž‰ Atekenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hao hande yakopiki enisolo tonu ameĚ±leĚ± ipiliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hali handaęž‰peketaęž‰ hunkupumaęž‰ homilieke.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do haleme wandaęž‰hali mandaneeki manutaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na homeke pa hataęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ welemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Yesu wonu piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 17ęž‰1-13, Luku 9ęž‰28-36)
\p 
\v 2 Kutupa hoto yunki mindiki hataęž‰ hao Yesumaęž‰ Pida Diaęž‰mesi Dioni tepo handaęž‰ meaataęž‰ pote tumiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua ikaęž‰siki haemekeme. Kutupa ikaęž‰ leke popeleke nane hataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ loke wonu piliekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ daumanu make paĚ±aĚ± peaataęž‰ hake wopu piekeme. Kenke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ dau hake peaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 4 Kutupa Elaidia Mosesi yaapo opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± pi pi lo haemekeme. Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰ koto disaipolo hali tepomaęž‰ handemekeme.
\v 5 Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Do paęž‰taęž‰ do halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Sale da tepo aęž‰eyamono lae laataęž‰ Homeke nakaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Mosesinaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ Elaidianaęž‰eki pea aęž‰eyamono lae leekeme.
\v 6 Pututumaęž‰ homemeke handaa Pidamaęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ hayekepate hone na wiekeme.
\p 
\v 7 Kutupa koamaęž‰ iki tuĚ± peaaso haenaęž‰ mo koa tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ laęž‰niaeyekeme dupa. Kototaęž‰ yaka puki piki wekie. Ipikaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰niaeyekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa koto kone koto hali tepomaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ pimikipate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handeke Yesu homeke handemekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Potenaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niaaso hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Oli handemeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na lapaęž‰peke. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ homa paa tiao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ alotaęž‰ Anaęž‰ pilieke leekeme.
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi wia miniki hataęž‰ otaęž‰ homa paa tiaalieke laa leaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 11 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimikime dupa. Pa ekipeke mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la Elaidia ipilieke lo halemepe lemekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la Elaidia otaęž‰ ipilieke. Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao winaęž‰yeke ipilieke laataęž‰ Mo hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ tanda tieke mu yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homao kiaalo peleme ekitaęž‰ eki eki pa laęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 13 Kutu piliepate IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Elaidia ambaęž‰la epeaęž‰pate pa mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pimikime leekeme.
\s1 Hoke temokomaęž‰ hoeyaeyeke weki Yesumaęž‰ epeaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 17ęž‰14-21, Luku 9ęž‰37-43)
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo mandane disaipolo haliweki haemeke alenaęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ koto haliwekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu hao popei yao yopua haemeke ekinaęž‰ handemekeme. Pa ekipeke mandane wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekitaęž‰ hande disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± kake neĚ±li pitolo hataęž‰ haemekeme.
\v 15 Kotaęž‰ koto kone mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Yesu handaataęž‰ penkilipa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ anke hao puaataęž‰ pi pi lemekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± alekenaęž‰ pi pi alemepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Yaka weki neke paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku epoaęž‰me. Hoke temoko pilaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ pi na lo halaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa mo hoke temokomaęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰pe miniki pitaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ mea lopao halaęž‰me leekeme. Koto ekimaęž‰ ya wekinaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ dako hankolomaęž‰ lia ipikaęž‰ kake lenkenaęž‰ lao halaęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ tindipulu bao daĚ±oĚ±la hao halaęž‰me la ombu alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ tolu linaęž‰yeke honke loaęž‰pate mo haliwekimaęž‰ anaęž‰ na piaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ hone na tulaaseme wandaęž‰halie. Nate ekipunaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± ombu hao hanope. Nate ekipunaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ kiteleme ekimanu meonope laataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku ipupe leekeme.
\v 20 Koto leeke mo wekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku mea pemekeme. Pate mo hoke temokomaęž‰ Yesu handaataęž‰ mo weki lu keayekeme. Kutu pieke mo wekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ dako hankolomaęž‰ liaaso haenaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ lopaaniao petepete pomiekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Do hautaęž‰ nate ekipunaęž‰ pea paęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Panake wekisiki yaęž‰pate kone pea piaęž‰me laataęž‰
\v 22 Hoke temokomaęž‰ hoto eleke eleke ti uleke paęž‰taęž‰ make ikali paęž‰taęž‰ make ipiki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ mea lopaatiki pu hayaęž‰me leekeme. Kutu piaęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 23 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aowe. Nakaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ epeaalueke. Wandaęž‰hali epi amedamaęž‰ hone tulaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hau paeyao peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa koto kone mo wekinaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hone tulaasome. Ya hone na tulaasoeki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 25 Yesumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopu aĚ±iĚ±ya epemekeeki handaataęž‰ mo hoke temoko hando alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pi na lao pi na opuaasaęž‰ temoko neke paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi alome. Koto weki minaęž‰paęž‰lao opolu bao yopuataęž‰ paa na hondaęž‰ pambaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 26 Koto pi opuaataęž‰ hoke temokomaęž‰ hoke eĚ± wi alo hataęž‰ mo weki wopu mea lu keaotaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao opolu bao yapeekeme. Kutu pieketaęž‰ mo weki otaęž‰ homeeke hali toko leke wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali eleke elekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lemekepate
\v 27 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kiki yolaęž‰ mea miniliaeyeke mo weki tiaeyekeme.
\p 
\v 28 Yesutaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaa ipiki honu make haenaęž‰ mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke temoko tolu liaęž‰peke na yeke ekitaęž‰ ekipape lemekeme.
\v 29 Koto lemeke Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kutupiki hoke temokotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰me ekimaęž‰ homeke tolu liaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki homa paa tiaalo pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki paa la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 17ęž‰22-23, Luku 9ęž‰43-45)
\p 
\v 30-31 Koto alenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaataęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane lombei pu pa puaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pi la haluekemaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki handaapenaęž‰ hone wiekeme. Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa waleekeme. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ haliweki oto paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ mea halieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki limikie. Kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ homiliepate hoto tepo wia paa daęž‰taalieke leekeme.
\v 32 Koto leekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hone na wimikime. Kutupa paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ na pimikime.
\s1 Tumiki hali epipe
\r (Maęž‰tiu 18ęž‰1-5, Luku 9ęž‰46-48)
\p 
\v 33 Kapeneami da paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰ aleke ataęž‰taęž‰ pimipe laa leekepate
\v 34 ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi na leke pa pitimikime. Ekipeke mo potaęž‰naęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰ epi tieke halaęž‰pe laa ataęž‰taęž‰ pimiki handaa pi na leke pa pitimikime.
\v 35 Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ pitiniao pitaęž‰ mo 12 haliweki wi laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ titinaęž‰ IĚ± halueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ hali hano laataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali hano lenaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 36 Koto laataęž‰ wekisiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo wekisiki hopulaęž‰ mea iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ dupiki wekisiki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ handaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰
\v 37 kotaęž‰ IĚ± kone handaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± handaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± homeke diaęž‰me. Hande IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰ hali make handaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰me laa leekeme.
\s1 Epimaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ na liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ekie
\r (Luku 9ęž‰49-50)
\p 
\v 38 Koto leeke handaa Dionimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Disao. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki alo hataęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu liaęž‰tiki piaęž‰eki handomaęž‰me. Koto sometaęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ na pomieke handaa saęž‰saęž‰ pumaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 39 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pa saęž‰saęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hali epimaęž‰ yaka biki alo hataęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ yaka biki na hoeyaalieke leekeme.
\v 40 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ halie leekeme.
\v 41 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ya biki melemeke handaataęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ikali naakaęž‰naęž‰ ipi kanakenaęž‰ holaęž‰ pamba iki kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yenki otaęž‰ milieke leekeme.
\s1 Hoke hau puluekemaęž‰ hone tiaasaęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 18ęž‰6-9, Luku 17ęž‰1-2)
\p 
\v 42 Hali epimaęž‰ do IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseme weki wandiki sunu homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau pinaęž‰ pu tiaenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halinaęž‰ make paęž‰taęž‰ toopi hombeleke mea tonkao oni dawala paęž‰taęž‰ mo hali mea lopaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 43 Nakaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ hoke hau puelenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto kiki tunkulu baapeke leekeme. Kiki homeke hataęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki mikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰pate kiki yaapo hataęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoelieke leekeme.
\v 44 (besi namba 48 handaęž‰peke)
\v 45 Nakaęž‰ ankemaęž‰ hoke hau puelenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke tunkulu baapeke leekeme. Anke homeke hataęž‰ hao halaęž‰eki mikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke leekeme. Anke yaapo hataęž‰ ti to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ pekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoelieke.
\v 46 (besi namba 48 handaęž‰peke)
\v 47 Nakaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ hoke hau puelenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ leke yokaęž‰ mea baapeke leekeme. Leke homeke hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ pekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke. Leke yaapo haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo ti to halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ neke mea lopaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoelieke leekeme.
\v 48 Koto alenaęž‰taęž‰ iki no haleme kimimanu na homo halememe. Kutupa mo ti to halaęž‰eki na hundinekepato halaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 49 Maęž‰naęž‰ hotekenaęž‰ damena pu alaęž‰ tupaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ ti talaęž‰eki pu lelieke leekeme.
\v 50 Epitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ tende paęž‰laęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ alu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo epitaęž‰ ekipa paa tende peaalipikipe leekeme. Ikaęž‰ kone epi wia hapaęž‰peke leekeme. Kutupa ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ pelia homu pu alu alu peaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\c 10
\s1 Tooli kaęž‰taęž‰alu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 19ęž‰1-12, Luku 16ęž‰18)
\p 
\v 1 Koto alenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao Yesu Diudia nane pua mo Diodani ikali yuma mone teaęž‰ nane make peekeme. Wandaęž‰hali wopu ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pa aęž‰pa mombelemekeme. Kutupa ambaęž‰ walo hayeke tupaęž‰ paa waleekeme.
\p 
\v 2 Mandane Paęž‰tisi haliwekimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ anke yololo hataęž‰ aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pimikime dupa. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yokeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ o kiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe o anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 3 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ eki pi ulaęž‰eki leekepe leekeme.
\v 4 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yokaęž‰laęž‰eki o kiaasaęž‰eki tameiyaęž‰naęž‰ wape pinaęž‰ laa kutupa yokenaęž‰ o kiaenaęž‰ lo hayekeme lemekeme.
\p 
\v 5 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ puki takaęž‰laaso haminaęž‰ koto hau peaęž‰paęž‰peke laa wape piekepate
\v 6 alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wepia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hali make haenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make haenaęž‰ leekeme laa
\v 7 Koto ekitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ateke inkiki yaapo minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipikaęž‰ maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ apaęž‰tao taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halipipikie.
\v 8 Kutupa ipilikitaęž‰ homeke kone halipipikie leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ yaapo diaęž‰me. Homeke kone halepeme leekeme.
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ apaęž‰taasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ halimaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰alu na peaenaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Da paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaa hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ hande leeke pi paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yokaataęž‰ o kiaotaęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo mupeke wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰la hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki otaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰maęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰la hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ weki wandiki sunu wamo pumaęž‰ pumaęž‰ piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 19ęž‰13-15, Luku 18ęž‰15-17)
\p 
\v 13-14 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ weki wandiki sunu Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wataenaęž‰yeke pimikime. Mo disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali saęž‰saęž‰ pimikipate Yesumaęž‰ handaataęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto weki wandiki sunu IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ lape. Saęž‰saęž‰ na piaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Dupiki weki wandiki sunumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handilimikie leekeme.
\v 15 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ mo wekiwandiki sunumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki minolo piteleme tupaęž‰ na mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ na hondo pambilimikie leekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo wekiwandiki sunu ipikaęž‰ kiki yaapomaęž‰ miniki hataęž‰ hopulu mea wamo pumaęž‰ pumaęž‰ piekeme.
\s1 Hamoko halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lotaęž‰ piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 19ęž‰16-30, Luku 18ęž‰18-30)
\p 
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya puaataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ tumiki yotuao pitaęž‰ lotaęž‰ piekeme dupa. Epeke Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Deto halaęž‰eki muluekemaęž‰ eki ponope leekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Ekipeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ Epeke halio alepe laataęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali aęž‰ndaęž‰ na aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰ homeketaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 19 Neketaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opueleme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ na liaęž‰peke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ hakopu na tunkulaęž‰peke. Pake na napeke. Yayapiki pi na lapeke. Na makeaapeke. Nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ apaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ pi opuaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 20 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Koto pimanu paeyao weki hataęž‰ kone opu haowaęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 21 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ homeke hau homeke na paęž‰laęž‰me. Neke pua nakaęž‰ wia hale alemanu paeyao maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambaataęž‰ mo natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ neketaęž‰ oli hepeni nane yenki tieke wialieke leekeme. Kutupa aęž‰pa ya hoki nane teliaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ koto leeke handaa mo halimaęž‰ wenoko homaęž‰niao kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ peekeme. Hamoko hali hayeke handaa piekeme.
\p 
\v 23 Yesumaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ moneao ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki handaataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hamoko wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ weleke we wotu pilimikie leekeme.
\v 24 Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto pi opua penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikipate Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa alotaęž‰ Ya weki titio. Hamoko wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 25 Kemolo maęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ noĚ±iĚ± kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yapaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pate hamoko halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ poluekemaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia wotu pomua ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kotaęž‰ epimaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 27 Yesumaęž‰ iki handa alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hau paeyao peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 28 Pidamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opie. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao minaęž‰paęž‰lao nakaęž‰ hoki nane teliolomaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 29-30 Koto leeke Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da ipikaęž‰ hameke titi ipikaęž‰ anaęž‰ titi ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki sunu make ipikaęž‰ kenkemanu make minaęž‰paęž‰laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make koto Pi Seliapo paęž‰taęž‰ make hone witolo hataęž‰ koto ekimanu minaęž‰paęž‰laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰ kone damanu 100 tupaęž‰ hameke titi make anaęž‰ titi make apaęž‰ amaęž‰ titi make wekiwandiki sunu make kenkemanu make 100 tupaęž‰ miliepate tanda minaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make milieke leekeme. Kutupa mo hao epolo paęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰ make deto halaęž‰eki milieke leekeme.
\v 31 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate ame do titinaęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ wetepe nane halimikie. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ titinaęž‰ halo pelimikie leekeme.
\s1 Homa paa tiaapeke ekinaęž‰ tanaęž‰ tepo la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 20ęž‰17-19, Luku 18ęž‰31-34)
\p 
\v 32 Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Diutuseleme da nane pulaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ opaęž‰liaaso haenaęž‰ Yesu ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ peekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomimikime. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ ipulu hataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ paleke teli mea epemekeme. Yesumaęž‰ hande 12 haliweki hosiki mopate leke pa hatuku pua ipiki minulu pimiki haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu koto haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ kini pu mea la hale hale pitolo alotaęž‰
\v 33 Opuaęž‰pe. Nikitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ Diutuseleme nane opaęž‰liaasomaęž‰me. Mo yeni peao haleme you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ make Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke mea dupa lelimikie. Neketaęž‰ homoelenaęž‰ lumeke lelimikie laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Diendaili haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mea halimikie laataęž‰
\v 34 kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki kitao ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ dopi taa yumbua bao limikie leekeme. Kutupa nate tepo wia paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ paa tiaalieke leekeme.
\s1 Diaęž‰mesi Dioni yaapomaęž‰ tieke haluekemaęž‰ lepekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 20ęž‰20-28)
\p 
\v 35 Sepedinaęž‰ eiyeke Diaęž‰mesi Dioni yaapomaęž‰ Yesu teke paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Dikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ honke lolupekemaęž‰ kuelenaęž‰e lepekeme.
\v 36 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Eki peaanope leekeme.
\p 
\v 37 Ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ biki tieke mea pitikaęž‰naęž‰ dikitaęž‰ homeke nakaęž‰ popeke nane paęž‰taęž‰liki nanemaęž‰ mea pitao maęž‰ndaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ nane paęž‰taęž‰liki nanemaęž‰ mea pitaalenaęž‰e lepekeme.
\p 
\v 38 Koto lepekepate Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipilikaęž‰ honke alepe ekitaęž‰ hone wotu na wiki hataęž‰ alepeme leekeme. IĚ±maęž‰ kaponaęž‰ nolue ekitaęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ make napaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. IĚ± bapitaisi peaaliaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipiliki make bapitaisi peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 39 Kutupa ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Diki anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me lepekeme.
\p Yesumaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kaponaęž‰ nolue ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ nelipipikie. IĚ± bapitaisi peaaluaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipiliki otaęž‰ bapitaisi peaalieke leekeme.
\v 40 Kutu piliepate ya popeke nane kiki hoeyaęž‰ nane kiki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ epimaęž‰ pitilipipikipe laataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo pitulu paęž‰laęž‰ ale wamo peao ulaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ halieke.
\p 
\v 41 Mo hande kiki yaapo haliwekimaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi Dioni yaapomaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ honke lepekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankemekeme.
\v 42 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo haliweki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handelememe. Diendaili wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kapomani tumiki haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tombuao halememe. Kutupa ikaęž‰ hali tieke tieke manumaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali Dupaęž‰pe laa pi wotu hapolo halememe leekeme.
\v 43 Koto tupaęž‰ lo halemepate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto hau na peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± tieke halueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hau peawalieke.
\v 44 Kutupa iki ameĚ±leĚ± hali epimaęž‰ IĚ± titinaęž‰ hali haluekee hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paeyaonaęž‰ hau peawalieke.
\v 45 Pa ekipeke mo Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke kone mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ yeke na epeeke yekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ e pokaaluekemaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki wopunaęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ yenki haluekemaęž‰ epeaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ leke holupiki halinaęž‰ leke kilaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 20ęž‰29-34, Luku 18ęž‰35-43)
\p 
\v 46 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Dietiko da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki make wandaęž‰hali wopu make Dietiko da nane minaęž‰paęž‰laaso haenaęž‰ Timeiyaęž‰sinaęž‰ eiyeketaęž‰ Batimeiyaęž‰si leke holupiki hali hataęž‰ mani honke loluekemaęž‰ yeke potaęž‰ nepokonaęž‰ pitiekeme.
\v 47 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesutaęž‰ yopulaęž‰me lemeke pi opuaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wi alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Oe. Yesuo. Deipidinaęž‰ tapake halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 48 Ipikaęž‰ leekeeki opuaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Pi na lapema laa saęž‰saęž‰ pimikipate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wi anekehapu alotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ tapake halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 49 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ pua potaęž‰ hopikinaęž‰ hando hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epenaęž‰ wi lape leekeme. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo leke holupiki hali wi laa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pa tiae. Neke wi alaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 50 Koto lemeke ipikaęž‰ make akaęž‰ holo baotaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ tiaa lupao Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.
\v 51 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Eki peaano hone paęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme. Mo leke holupiki halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Ya leke yaapo ki laae leekeme.
\v 52 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke pue. Nakaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰me leekeme. Kutupa koto kone ipikaęž‰ leke yaapo epeeketaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea peekeme.
\c 11
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Kini Hali tupaęž‰ Diutuseleme lepolonaęž‰ epeekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰1-11, Luku 19ęž‰28-40, Dioni 12ęž‰12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Diutuseleme da teke paęž‰taęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ Betepeisi Bedani da yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekeme. Mo da yaapotaęž‰ mo Olipi ti polu haemeke peiyenenaęž‰ hayekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 2 Mo koto nane halaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ da opolo pulu hataęž‰ kuta kone donki maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ panake donkisiki homeke wakapenaęž‰ endia haenaęž‰ handilipipikie leekeme. Koto donki maęž‰naęž‰siki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ ambaęž‰ na pita handeke donkie laa Wakapaęž‰ holaęž‰ mea aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 3 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ Ekipeke pitelepepe leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke. Tekehalimaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me lapaęž‰peke. Wetepenaęž‰ kuta kone maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea epenaęž‰ lelieke lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\p 
\v 4 Koto leeke puaataęž‰ mo donki maęž‰naęž‰ potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ endia lepolo potaęž‰naęž‰ haenaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaataęž‰ kelepaęž‰ mipikime.
\v 5 Kaęž‰laęž‰paaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ koto alenaęž‰ haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ hololo haenaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo donkisiki kelepelepe ekitaęž‰ eki puluekemaęž‰ kelepelepepe lemekeme.
\v 6 Kotaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ lepekeme. Leeke ekitaęž‰ opuaataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ paęž‰naęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 7 Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ mea pepeketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ daumanu mea mo donki sikinaęž‰ hokinaęž‰ yamaemeketaęž‰ Yesu manda aęž‰meiya pitiekeme.
\v 8 Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ daumanu lepolonaęž‰ yamomaęž‰ yamomaęž‰ pimikime. Kutupa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ katake mendia wiki ti palekemanu tondopaęž‰ mea yamomaęž‰ yamomaęž‰ pimikime.
\v 9 Titinaęž‰ pemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make wetepenaęž‰ pemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ wi la alu alu pitolo alotaęž‰
\p Hosaęž‰naęž‰e. Taęž‰naęž‰e. Tekehalinaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laenaęž‰e laa
\v 10 Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ Deipidi ipikaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki ipulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi lamanaęž‰e. Hepeni nane Hosaęž‰naęž‰ pi lamanaęž‰e. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki aęž‰meiyaomanaęž‰e lemekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Yesumaęž‰ Diutuseleme da opolo pua tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handomaęž‰ handomaęž‰ peaataęž‰ nate ambaęž‰ paeyeke handaataęž‰ timbaęž‰ lapeke yeeke mo disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Bedani da nane pemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo nose ti paęž‰taęž‰ kiliki na aęž‰ilipikie leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰18-19)
\p 
\v 12 Kutupa da kaęž‰laęž‰peeke haenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Bedani da minaęž‰paęž‰lao paa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.
\v 13 Potaęž‰naęž‰ puaataęž‰ nose ti homeke katake mendia wieke ekinaęž‰ mopate leke hataęž‰ handaataęž‰ kiliki aęž‰elaęž‰patemaęž‰ handolo peekepate teke paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ pa katakemanu homeke handeekeme. Mo nose kiliki aęž‰eyaęž‰peke nate aĚ±iĚ± diaęž‰yeke piekeme.
\v 14 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo nose paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kilikimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na talo nelieke leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ koto leeke pitaęž‰ opimikime.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ peekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰12-17, Luku 19ęž‰45-48, Dioni 2ęž‰13-22)
\p 
\v 15 Diutuseleme da paęž‰taęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ koto da paęž‰taęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu hambo haemeke haliweki hamaęž‰ nane tolu liaataęž‰ mo mani topo pu haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ teipolomanu make melipu bamanu hambo haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ pitieke alemanu hoilaęž‰minaęž‰ lopaeyekeme.
\v 16 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo da puku tokaęž‰laęž‰ mea tia yopuaęž‰tiki peaamaęž‰naęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pitolo leekeme.
\v 17 Kutupieke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi wala iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Baibolonaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka dataęž‰ kenke paeyao wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ yeni pu halo paęž‰laęž‰ da halaęž‰me laa wape pa ulaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do dataęž‰ pake no pamboloendi piteleme da haenaęž‰ alememe leekeme.
\p 
\v 18 Wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ waleeke pimanu opuaataęž‰ penkili pimiki handaataęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipiki lu alu palo pimiki potaęž‰ weimikime.
\v 19 Kutupa nate pambolo haenaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± teke da minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemekeme.
\s1 Nose ti homeeke ekinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke ekinaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰20-22)
\p 
\v 20 Da kaęž‰laęž‰peketaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ yopulu hataęž‰ hande nose ti handemekepate katake teke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ paeyao hapua hayekeeki handemekeme.
\v 21 Pidamaęž‰ hone wia ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio. Handaęž‰e. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pimaęž‰ kone hoeyaeye nose ti koto hapua halaęž‰ handaęž‰e leeketaęž‰
\v 22 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hapaęž‰peke.
\v 23 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Hali epimaęž‰ oli pote paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ kone tiao mo dawala paęž‰taęž‰ pua lopaęž‰peke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ hone ti na yokeke pa ipikaęž‰ dupilieke leeke pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ pilieke laa homeke hone witolo hataęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hali paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pinaęž‰ lelieke leekeme.
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ yeni pitolo hataęž‰ honke lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ambaęž‰ mea wia halome hone wia hataęž‰ milimikie leekeme.
\v 25 Kutupa make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ yeni pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hone pa upaleke hataęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau tombuao pa paeyaapaęž‰peke leekeme. Ikaęž‰ hepeni nane halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaenaęž‰yeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰eki paeyaapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 26 [Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki na paeyaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hepeni nane halaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰eki make na paeyaalieke leekeme.]
\s1 Epimaęž‰ neke biki halo piaęž‰pe lemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰23-27, Luku 20ęž‰1-8)
\p 
\v 27 Yesu ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Diutuseleme da nane paa puaataęž‰ tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pulu haenaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua alotaęž‰
\v 28 Hande pu haleeki manutaęž‰ ekipa pipe o epimaęž‰ neke wele peaeyaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ opua la kimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pu halo hau manutaęž‰ IĚ± wele peao halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki la kulueke.
\v 30 Dionimaęž‰ bapitaisi peao hayaęž‰ hautaęž‰ hepeni nane ekipe o kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ekipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 31 Koto pi opuaataęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi lemekeme dupa. Hepeni nane ekie lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ Kotaęž‰ Dionimaęž‰ lo hayaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ ekipeke na miniki haemepe lelieke laa
\v 32 Kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ekie lolumaęž‰pe lemekepate wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Dionitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halo hayaęž‰ halie lo halemeke handaa mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme.
\v 33 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki na handolomaęž‰me lemekeme. Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make yaka pu halo haumanu IĚ± wele peao halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ iki na la kulueke leekeme.
\c 12
\s1 Hoke haliwekimaęž‰ e handeteke haemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 21ęž‰33-46, Luku 20ęž‰9-19)
\p 
\v 1 Koto laa Yesumaęž‰ onkolumaęž‰ laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ waini e pokaataęž‰ pape pea mo waini kilikimanu dikili pulu pieke alenaęž‰ kenke awaataęž‰ ti hokulu mea aęž‰meiyao nokaęž‰pa oli manda hataęž‰ e handeteke haenaęž‰ da aęž‰eyekeme. Dupa pea ipikaęž‰ e pokaaseme haliweki mea haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane peekeme.
\v 2 Bapinaęž‰ mo e teke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ hande e pokao haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ kilikimanu mandaneeki meaenaęž‰yeke tapaeyekeme.
\v 3 Koto haliwekimaęž‰ mo e pokaasaęž‰ hali meaataęž‰ yombua bao kiki hameke tapaemekeme.
\v 4 Kutupa e teke halimaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaeyekepate mo haliwekimaęž‰ koto somenaęž‰ amboke yombua baotaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ tieke homaemekeme.
\v 5 E teke halimaęž‰ paa maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapaeyekepate otaęž‰ limikime. Koto haliwekimaęž‰ mandaneeki wopu paęž‰taęž‰ make kutu pimikime. Mandane ekimanu yombua baotaęž‰ mandane ekimanu otaęž‰ limikime.
\p 
\v 6 Mo e teke hali yaapotaęž‰ homeketaęž‰ pa hayekeme. Ipikaęž‰ puki piki weki homeke pa hayekeme. Paeyaaso hataęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke tapaaso hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka wekinaęž‰ pi opua homu pea halimikie leekeme.
\v 7 Koto leekepate mo e pokao haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ e teke halinaęž‰ anke teke mulu paęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ alemaęž‰ Lumanaęž‰ bape lemekeme. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mumanaęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 8 Kutupa mo hande halinaęž‰ eiyeke mea otaęž‰ liaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke mo e tikene nane mea baemekeme leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo e teke halimaęž‰ eki piliaęž‰pe laa Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ mo e pokao haemeke haliweki otaęž‰ lia paeyaotaęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokao haenaęž‰ lelieke laataęž‰
\v 10 Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pi do ekitaęž‰ na yataęž‰pelemepe.
\q1 Mo da aęž‰eyo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ baemeke toopitaęž‰ da keneme nane otaęž‰ teke toopi ulaęž‰me.
\q1 
\v 11 Kutu piaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ piaęž‰me. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaataęž‰ penkili polomaęž‰me
\q1 laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 12 Mo hande yeni peao haemeke teke haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make paeyaomaęž‰ do onkolumaęž‰ pitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ Yesu mininaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ taapemekepate wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemeke handaataęž‰ Yesu minaęž‰paęž‰lao pemekeme.
\s1 Sisanaęž‰ dakisi mani
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰15-22, Luku 20ęž‰20-26)
\p 
\v 13 Pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane Paęž‰tisi haliweki make Hetodinaęž‰ hoki nane telimiki haliweki make Yesunaęž‰ pi ta molo penaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ tapaemekeme.
\v 14 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu lo hale halie. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ opolomaęž‰me lemekeme. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na u haleme. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mandake hau piki wandaęž‰halie laakaęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi homeke walo haleme la alotaęž‰ Mo Kapomani tieke Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ dakisi mani halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe o hoelaęž‰pe. Mani halomonope o na halomonope laa lemekeme.
\p 
\v 15 Koto lemeketaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kekeke haemekeeki handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ya anke ekipeke yolaęž‰lemepe leekeme. Toopi poeke homeke handono mea ipupe leekeme.
\v 16 Homeke mea aęž‰pa haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto suĚ±aĚ± suĚ±aĚ± ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epinaęž‰ leke popelekepe leekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Sisanaęž‰ ekie lemekeme.
\v 17 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Sisanaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ Sisa paęž‰taęž‰ pa mea halaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa halaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ koto pi opuaataęž‰ penkili pimikime.
\s1 Homaa paa tiaalo paęž‰laęž‰ pi
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰23-33, Luku 20ęž‰27-40)
\p 
\v 18 Mandane Saęž‰dusi haliweki Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ epemekeme. Koto tapakemaęž‰ otaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa na tiaalieke lo haemeke haliwekie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰
\v 19 Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Mosesimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ dupa wape piekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mupeke hameketaęž‰ wandaęž‰ pa haenaęž‰ weki wandiki na mendiki homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto wetepe nane halimaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kosaęž‰piki meaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homeeke hamekenaęž‰ weki wandikimanu mendiao haenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke wape piekeme leekeme.
\v 20 Kutupataęž‰ hameketiti watake hataęž‰ haemekeme. Mupeke wekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰ meaataęž‰ weki wandiki na mendiki homeekeme.
\v 21 Kutupa hoki nane wekimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ meaataęž‰ weki wandiki na mendiki homeekeme. Kutupa koto hoki nane weki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piekeme.
\v 22 Watake hataęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ miekepate mo wandaęž‰ pa haenaęž‰ weki wandiki na mendiki pa haenaęž‰ homeke homeke lo homemekeme. Kutupa homo paeyaeyeke nanetaęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰ make homeekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa wandaęž‰hali paa tialimi natenaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ haliepe. Pa ekipeke mo watake hataęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ homeke kone mimikime lemekeme.
\p 
\v 24 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi lo hoeyaasememe. Pa ekipeke mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ ekimanu na handelememe. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pu halaęž‰ ekimanu make na handelememe.
\v 25 Ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paa tiaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ na miki hali na peke oli hepeni nane enisolo tapake haleme tupaęž‰ pa hao halimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo hande homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa tiaalo pelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ alome dupa. Mosesimaęž‰ wape pieke bukanaęž‰ mo hande pa hayeke ti sikinaęž‰ kone ti to hayekeeki na yataęž‰pemepe. Do manaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ leekeme dupa. IĚ±taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make Aisaęž‰kenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make Dieikopenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make halome leekeme.
\v 27 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do leaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ homolo peleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Deto halo peleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰e laa laęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone u hoeyaasememe leekeme.
\s1 Titinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰34-40, Luku 10ęž‰25-28)
\p 
\v 28 Kutupa mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi pi lemekeeki opitolo hataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi epeke tupaęž‰ hombo peaaso leekeeki opuaataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Mo hande pi ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handoekipe leekeme.
\p 
\v 29 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Titinaęž‰eki doe. Isulai wandaęž‰halio. Opuaęž‰pe laęž‰laęž‰me. Tekehali Kodaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali homeke halaęž‰me.
\v 30 Kutupa mo Tekehali nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ puki paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ temoko paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ hone witeleeki paeyaomaęž‰ make nakaęž‰ honkopu haseeki paeyaomaęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homo hapaęž‰pekee laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 31 Wetepenaęž‰eki doe. Neke paęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ kone aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homele tupaęž‰ da wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo hapaęž‰pekee laęž‰laęž‰me laa koto hande pi ulaęž‰eki yaapotaęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ekie. Mandaneeki manutaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 32 Kutupa mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu hayeke halimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Otaęž‰ aleme. Kodaęž‰ homeke halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ leme. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me ipiki homekee.
\v 33 Kutupa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puki paeyaomaęž‰ make hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyaomaęž‰ make honkopu hasaęž‰eki paeyaomaęž‰ make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ niki kone aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ da wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ kone aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ekie leekeme. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yanka halaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyao make liaa halaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make koto ekitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ekie leekeme.
\p 
\v 34 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ hone wopu wia epeke tupaęž‰ leekeeki opuaataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki teke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme leekeme. Koto leaęž‰eki hoki nanetaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ paalaęž‰ pieke handaa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lotaęž‰ paa na piekeme.
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ tapake apaęž‰taęž‰ epipe
\r (Maęž‰tiu 22ęž‰41-46, Luku 20ęž‰41-44)
\p 
\v 35 Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ Deipidinaęž‰ tapake wekie laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ekipa laęž‰laęž‰pe laa
\v 36 Deipidimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ la halolo haenaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ yaka Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ leekeeki dupa.
\q1 Nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki nakaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ mea pitaanoyeke yaka popeke nane kikinaęž‰ pitaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 37 Kotaęž‰ Deipidimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ Yaka Tekehalie laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake wekitaęž‰ ekipa haliepe leekeme. Mo wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pi taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa opimikime.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo tapake manunaęž‰ haumanu lo kelaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 23ęž‰1-36, Luku 20ęž‰45-47)
\p 
\v 38 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haleme haliwekinaęž‰ hau wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke leekeme. Hokulupiki daumanu pambao pomu hataęž‰taęž‰ makedinaęž‰ hatiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi la halenaęž‰ hone u halememe.
\v 39 Kutupa pi hotu haemeke damanu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pituluekemaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki handenaęž‰ hone wia epeke sea manunaęž‰ pitu halememe. Ne pambaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make epeke haupiki seanaęž‰ pituluekemaęž‰ hone u halememe leekeme.
\v 40 Kutupa kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰wekinaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ pa meaataęž‰ kutu pitolo kone handaenaęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ yeni pu hokulu peao halememe leekeme. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke milimikie leekeme.
\s1 Kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mani haleekeeki
\r (Luku 21ęž‰1-4)
\p 
\v 41 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ mani pambo haemeke bokosi teke paęž‰taęž‰ ti lao pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mani lopaemekeeki handeekeme. Hamoko wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ mani wopu mea aęž‰pa lopaemekeme.
\v 42 Wetepenaęž‰ natehali kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ sikimaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ manisiki yaapo 2 toeamaęž‰ handekeeki mea aęž‰pa lopaeyekeme.
\v 43 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰ mepi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do natehali kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰ sikimaęž‰ mea aęž‰pa lopaeyaęž‰ eki sikitaęž‰ tiekee. Mo mea aęž‰pa lopaaseme wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hosiki alesikie.
\v 44 Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mani tieke putupu mea putupiliki wimiki ekimanu mea lopaememe. Kutu pimikipate do wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ natehali hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wiaęž‰ hayekeeki paeyao mea lopaeyaęž‰me leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ ne hambaęž‰pekeeki kone mea lopaeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\c 13
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰1-14, Luku 21ęž‰5-19)
\p 
\v 1 Yesumaęž‰ mo tembolo da minaęž‰paęž‰lao hamaęž‰ nane opolu baaso haenaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali homekemaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halio. Handaęž‰e. Do toopimanu tieke tiekee leekeme. Do da tiekemanu make seliapo seliapoe leekeme.
\v 2 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do da tiekemanu handelepe. Toopi manda maęž‰ndaęž‰ na tapaęž‰ pelia hataęž‰ paeyao otaęž‰ lopilieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 3 Yesutaęž‰ oli Olipi ti polu peiyene paęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo da handaęž‰moneao pitinaęž‰ Pida Diaęž‰mesi Dioni Aęž‰ndutu make ikaęž‰ honumake sikimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pea alotaęž‰
\v 4 La kie lemekeme. Hande le ekitaęž‰ handimaęž‰ ipiliepe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime. Kutupa ipuluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ eki hau pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki handulumaęž‰pe laa lotaęž‰ pimikime.
\p 
\v 5 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la halolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki hatuku pu hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke.
\v 6 Haliweki wopumaęž‰ yaka biki alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Ketisoe lelimikie. Kutupa wandaęž‰hali wopu hatuku pu hoeyaalimikie leekeme.
\v 7 Teke paęž‰taęž‰ make papate make aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitelememe pi opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pulu pelemepate paelo paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± diaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰ kenke homeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tiaotaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie. Naęž‰sinolo Kapomani homekenaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tiaotaęž‰ Naęž‰sinolo Kapomani maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pilimikie leekeme. Yu kenke taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu yu momeni wotu pilimikie. Kutupa da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane halo peleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ teaęž‰ ki ipilieke leekeme. Kutupulu pelemeeki manutaęž‰ tandamaęž‰ homolo peleme ekitaęž‰ kini pu milimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ iki mo pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ mea hatuku pelimikie. Pi hotu halaęž‰ damanu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ iki yombu mea baalimikie. Kutupa yaka bikinaęž‰ kapomani you halimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make Kini haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu halemekeeki la halimikie leekeme.
\p 
\v 10 Kutu puluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande Pi Seliapo kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ walimikie leekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ iki mea hatuku pemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lolo peleme pi ambaęž‰la hone bao hapaęž‰peke. Koto pitaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ la kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotoeki lapaęž‰peke leekeme. Ikaęž‰ kone pi na lelimikie. Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ lawaalieke.
\v 12 Kutupa hameke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kamesiki otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ lelieke. Atekemaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ weki kone otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ laataęž‰ weki wandiki tonumaęž‰ make tiaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ateke inkiki yaapo otaęž‰ homenaęž‰ lelimikie leekeme.
\v 13 Yaka biki menelemeke handaa wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ iki otaęž‰ kiaalimikie. Kutu pilimipate hali epimaęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke paelo paęž‰laęž‰ tombonaęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki milieke leekeme.
\s1 Hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ ale ipilieke
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰15-28, Luku 21ęž‰20-24)
\p 
\v 14 Hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ aletaęž‰ mo hoke ale wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ mea wia haenaęž‰ handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Do pi yataęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ hone winaęž‰e mo Diudia nane halo peleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo potemanu paęž‰taęž‰ pindipa penaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 15 Da holunaęž‰ haliaęž‰ halimaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ mea poluekemaęž‰ da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ na hondaęž‰ pambenaęž‰e.
\v 16 Enaęž‰ haliaęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ dau mea poluekemaęž‰ hoki na lekelenaęž‰e leekeme.
\p 
\v 17 Weki pitiki wandaęž‰weki make andu halimi wandaęž‰weki make koto nate manunaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰e laataęž‰
\v 18 koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo kosaęž‰ kinaęž‰taęž‰ na epenaęž‰yeke yeni peaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme. Koto nate manunaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki hone matekeeki ipilieke leekeme.
\v 19 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki koto tupaęž‰ ambaęž‰ na epeekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wepia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰ kini pa pua ame do make diaęž‰me. Wetepenaęž‰ make kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki koto tupaęž‰ na ipilieke leekeme.
\v 20 Koto natenaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao homolo pelemepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto natemanu tunkulinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipekepe. Ipikaęž‰ talopu maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone wiaataęž‰ koto natemanu tunkulinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 21 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Handaęž‰pe. Ketiso do ane halaęž‰me o Handaęž‰pe. Ketiso mo nane halaęž‰me leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 22 Yayapiki Ketiso haliweki make yayapiki potopede haliweki make aęž‰paataęž‰ iki penkilipulu peleme alemanu make wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make walaataęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ talopu maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali kone kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pu hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ walimikie.
\v 23 Kutu pilimipate wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Epolo paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu paeyao ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kuaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Wetepenaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke ipilieke
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰29-31, Luku 21ęž‰25-28)
\p 
\v 24 Koto nate manunaęž‰ mo hande kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo pelemeeki hone matekeeki paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ oli nate make timbaęž‰ lo pambaataęž‰ oli sumbaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± na pilieke.
\v 25 Oli hombulankaęž‰manu make ya nane hao hondaęž‰ pa pa pu lopaęž‰tiki pilieke. Kutupa oli ya nane wele peaasaęž‰ ekimanu laęž‰maęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ pupa wilimikie.
\v 26 Koto natenaęž‰taęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ koa tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ wele wotu pitolo hataęž‰ make paĚ±aĚ± tieke pitolo hataęž‰ make epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki handilimikie leekeme.
\v 27 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo enisolomanu tapa tapa peaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ talopu maęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ nate opaęž‰laęž‰ nane make nate pambaęž‰laęž‰ nane make oni nane make oli nane make paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ mea mombelaalieke leekeme.
\s1 Handeteke hapaęž‰peke laa onkolumaęž‰ leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰32-35, Luku 21ęž‰29-33)
\p 
\v 28 Nose timaęž‰ pu halaęž‰eki hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ipikaęž‰ paleke adaęž‰ pea katake tindiki lia kelepeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ bapi ipuluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me hone u halememe leekeme.
\v 29 Kutupa make hande loaęž‰ alemanu ipulaęž‰eki handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ tekepaęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me laa potaęž‰ kake paęž‰taęž‰ hande nate kone aęž‰pa halaęž‰me hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 30 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ paeyao na homeke halimi pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ loaęž‰ alemanu paeyao ambaęž‰ ipilieke leekeme.
\v 31 Oli ya do kenke yaapotaęž‰ paelo paęž‰laęž‰pate yaka pi lo haloeki manutaęž‰ na paelieke leekeme.
\s1 Epolo paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰me laa leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 24ęž‰36-44)
\p 
\v 32 Kutu piliepate hande loaęž‰ nate epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰me. Nate handopaęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰eki make maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handaęž‰laęž‰me. Oli hepeni nane haleme enisolo tapakemaęž‰ make Eiyekemaęž‰ make na handelemaęž‰pate Atekemaęž‰ homeke handaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 33 Ikitaęž‰ uĚ± na peliki yu wia hapaęž‰peke. Mo epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ditaęž‰ iki mateleme.
\v 34 Do tupaęž‰e leekeme. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ kimisu peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ da minaęž‰paęž‰lao ipikaęž‰ e pokaaseme haliwekimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ laa ikaęž‰ kaukata walaa tapa tapa pea kutupa potaęž‰ kake handeteke halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ wopu handeteke haenaęž‰ lelieke leekeme.
\v 35 Koto ekinaęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Hande da teke halinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ditaęž‰ iki mataęž‰laęž‰me. Timbaęž‰ timbaęž‰ alo haenaęž‰pe o butaęž‰ hokinaęž‰pe o kokaęž‰laęž‰ eĚ± alo haenaęž‰pe o da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso nanepe.
\v 36 Ikitaęž‰ uĚ± peliolo haminaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ kutaa kone aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 37 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alo ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Handeteke hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\c 14
\s1 Yesu luekemaęž‰ potaęž‰ weimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰1-5, Luku 22ęž‰1-2, Dioni 11ęž‰45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke nate make Na Pombei Yaake Palaowa Nalaęž‰ di make hone uluekemaęž‰ ne pambaaluekemaęž‰ nate yaapo titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰laęž‰ wiekeme. Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make Yesu aęž‰mbao mina lu pimiki potaęž‰ weimikime.
\v 2 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ne pambaaso haenaęž‰taęž‰ diaęž‰me. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankaapaęž‰naęž‰ lemekeme. Kutupa potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ weimikime.
\s1 Wandaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ younaęž‰ senisi ikali holaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰6-13, Dioni 12ęž‰1-8)
\p 
\v 3 Yesutaęž‰ Bedani da puaataęž‰ kindi yeni hayeke hali Saimononaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ ne nalo pitinaęž‰ wandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰baęž‰setaęž‰ toopi kanake homeke mea epeekeme. Mo kanake paęž‰taęž‰ senisi totopo pikieki seliapo pambeekeme. Koto senisinaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Nadae. Yenki tieke alee. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ kanake yambaęž‰laęž‰ liaataęž‰ hande senisitaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ younaęž‰ holaeyekeme.
\v 4 Kutu piekepate mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone mineke pankolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto senisitaęž‰ ekipeke pa hameke hoeyaasaęž‰pe.
\v 5 Do senisi maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hambeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ 300 kina meaęž‰peke yolo piaęž‰me. Kutupa mo manitaęž‰ natehali wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke yolo piaęž‰me lemekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone witolo hataęž‰ tandapiki pi lemekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Koto lemekepate Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Koto wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi na leke minaęž‰paęž‰lape. Pa ekipeke ipiki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaasemepe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau piaęž‰me.
\v 7 Natehali wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ nate paeyao iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao halimikie. Kutupa ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ epeke haumanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hoto paeyao na hao halueke.
\v 8 Do wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ piaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki piaęž‰me. Yaka loke aĚ±iĚ± na hoitelemepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ senisi ambaęž‰laęž‰ holaeyaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 9 Kutupa iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ Pi Seliapo walaęž‰tiki pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do wandaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ piaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone winaęž‰yeke walaęž‰tiki pilimikie leekeme.
\s1 Diudasimaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lomba wiekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰14-16, Luku 22ęž‰3-6)
\p 
\v 10 Kutupa Isekatioti hali Diudasimaęž‰ mo hande 12 haliweki hayeke halimaęž‰ kone Yesu linaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombuluekemaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.
\v 11 Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi opuaataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homemekeme. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mani haluekemaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wimikime. Kutupa yeni peao haemeke teke haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu mininaęž‰yeke Diudasimaęž‰ potaęž‰ weiyekeme.
\s1 Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ ne nemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰17-25, Luku 22ęž‰7-14,21-23, Dioni 13ęž‰21-30)
\p 
\v 12 Na Pombei Yaake Palaowa Ne pambaeyaęž‰ pitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ natenaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke natenaęž‰ sipisipi ikiki lu haemeke pitaęž‰ kone Yesunaęž‰ disaipolo haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke nate hone uelenaęž‰yeke ne pambaalumaęž‰eki noelenaęž‰yeke hando paęž‰taęž‰ pua da wamo peamonope lemekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo tapaaso hataęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo daoni nane puaataęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ikali kanake homeke tia ipulu hataęž‰ ipiliki mandaęž‰hande pilieke. Kutupa mo hali teli mea puaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 14 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto da teke hali paęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapaęž‰peke. Walaęž‰laęž‰ Halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yaka disaipolo haliweki IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± Lombei Pupa Yapeeke natenaęž‰ ne nolo polomaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ hando paęž‰taęž‰pe lapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 15 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ manda nane wamo pea ulaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ tieke walieke leekeme.
\p 
\v 16 Mo disaipolo hali yaapomaęž‰ daoni nane puaataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaeyekeme. Kutupa mo hande Lombei Pupa Yapeeke natenaęž‰ ne hone uluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne wamo pipikime.
\p 
\v 17 Timbaęž‰ alo haenaęž‰ Yesu mandane 12 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± koto paęž‰taęž‰ opolo pemekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa ne nalo pitinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. IĚ± mininaęž‰yeke IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± do ne nalaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ kone aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰lieke leekeme.
\v 19 Koto leeke handaa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰pe laęž‰tiki pimikime.
\v 20 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki 12 haliweki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke halimaęž‰ pilieke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ palaowa tenke laaso metekinaęž‰ kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make palaowa tenke laasaęž‰me leekeme.
\v 21 Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ homenaęž‰ aęž‰ndu halimipate pa Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke mininaęž‰yeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰taęž‰e. Na mendiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me leekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ne ikali haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰26-30, Luku 22ęž‰14-20, 1 Kotindi 11ęž‰23-25)
\p 
\v 22 Ne nalo pitinaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ palaowa mea Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae laa pindi pindi pea iki paęž‰taęž‰ hala alotaęž‰ Mipe. Dotaęž‰ ya loke mindikie leekeme.
\v 23 Kutupa kapo mea keiyae laakaęž‰naęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hale hale piekeme. Iki paeyaomaęž‰ mo kaponaęž‰ nemekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Pi laęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ yaka we doe. Wandaęž‰hali paeyao epeaaluekemaęž‰ yaka we lopilieke laa
\v 25 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Do nalomaęž‰ waini ikali IĚ±taęž‰ paataęž‰ na neke hao wetepenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ panakeeki nolueke leekeme.
\p 
\v 26 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ emeli maęž‰ndaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo Olipi Pote paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\s1 Pida paęž‰taęž‰ Yaka biki hoeyaalipikie la haleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰31-35, Luku 22ęž‰31-34, Dioni 13ęž‰36-38)
\p 
\v 27 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki paeyaomaęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰lalimikie. Mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Sipisipi handeteke hao halaęž‰ hali lueke. Kutupa mo sipisipi titi mandane mandane pindipa pomu keaalimikie wape paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\v 28 Kutu pilimipate IĚ± paa mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ambaęž‰la Kaęž‰lili nane polueke. Ikitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 29 Koto leeke Pidamaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ neke minaęž‰paęž‰laemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ neke na minaęž‰paęž‰lalueke leekeme.
\v 30 Yesumaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Ame timba kone kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ hoto yaapo peao e aĚ±iĚ± na leke haenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto tepo yaka biki ambaęž‰la hoeyaalipikie leekeme.
\v 31 Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ pi takaęž‰lakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diki mandakenaęž‰ homopono leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kone nakaęž‰ biki na hoeyaalueke leekeme. Kutupa mo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ lemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Kesemaęž‰ni e paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni piekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰36-46, Luku 22ęž‰39-46)
\p 
\v 32 Yesu make mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± Kesemaęž‰ni e nane pemekeme. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pulu pono ikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 33 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ Pida Diaęž‰mesi Dioni ameda hatuku puaataęž‰ koto kone ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ wopu miekeme.
\v 34 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yaka pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolome. Homeke nono pea halome. Ikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ yu wia hataęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke leekeme.
\v 35 Kutupa hosiki mopate leke puaataęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ peliniao yeni piekeme. Ipikaęž‰ yeni pieke ekitaęž‰ dupa piekeme. Anaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki ipulaęž‰eki mone yaae laa yeni piekeme.
\v 36 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ya apaęž‰o. Hau paeyao nakanaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Do IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰ kapo IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na epenaęž‰ lapeke. Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Nakaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki homekee leekeme.
\p 
\v 37 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰paataęž‰ mo haliweki u peliekeeki handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Saimonoo. Polu pili leekeme. Hosiki handeteke hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe.
\v 38 Handeteke hataęž‰ yeni pu hapaęž‰peke. La handaęž‰laęž‰eki aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. Pukimaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰pate lokemaęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homa adaadaęž‰ pea witaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 39 Kutupa paa pua yeni pitolo hataęž‰ mo hande pimanu kone paa leekeme.
\v 40 Paa aęž‰pa handeekepate ikitaęž‰ pelimikieki handeekeme. Ikaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ u pamba wimiki handaa pimikime. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hombo peaaluekemaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ hone na wimikime.
\p 
\v 41 Yesumaęž‰ hoto tepo peao aęž‰pa iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ pa peliake u pitaęž‰ hoto pitaęž‰ pimi. Anaęž‰e. Mo handaęž‰e. Aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeke IĚ±taęž‰ hoke hau pu haleme haliwekimaęž‰ mininaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 42 Pomanaęž‰ tiaape. IĚ± mininaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombaęž‰laęž‰ hali koto ipulaęž‰ handaęž‰e leekeme.
\s1 Haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu minimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰47-56, Luku 22ęž‰47-53, Dioni 18ęž‰3-12)
\p 
\v 43 Koto pi alo haenaęž‰ kone Diudasitaęž‰ mo hande 12 haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hayeke hali kone epeekeme. Kutupa Diudasi ameĚ±leĚ± haliweki wopumaęž‰ kepete tieke make dolo make miniki epemekeme. Mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make mo tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make tapaeyeke handaa epemekeme.
\v 44 Yesu mininaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeeke halimaęž‰ mo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ patehau ambaęž‰ waleekeeki dupa. IĚ±maęž‰ nunu puluaęž‰ halitaęž‰ ipikie. Koto hali daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniki hao hatuku mea pupe leekeme.
\p 
\v 45 Kutupa Diudasimaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰ kutaa kone Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ pua ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Tekehalio laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu nunu piekeme.
\v 46 Mo haliwekimaęž‰ nunu piekeeki handaataęž‰ Yesu meaataęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniki haemekeme.
\v 47 Kutu pimikipate koto paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kepete poneke hokulu yolaęž‰ mea mo yeni peao haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ e pa pokao hayeke hali pokeekepate katake tunkulu poka lopaeyekeme.
\v 48 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ pake hali patemaęž‰ kepete tieke dolo make miniki aęž‰pa pimipe.
\v 49 Nate wopu IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± pi walo haowaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ minimime. Kutu pimipate mo Baibolo bukamaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki yaalieke leekeme.
\v 50 Kutupa disaipolo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ Yesu minaęž‰paęž‰lao pindipa pemekeme.
\p 
\v 51 Wekihali homekemaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu teli mea peekeme. Koto wekitaęž‰ pa dau homeke yameekeme. Kutupa haliwekimaęž‰ ipiki daęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ miniki haemekepate
\v 52 hande dau leisi minolo haenaęž‰ loke homeke pindipa peekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ mo yeni peao hayeke teke hali paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰57-68, Luku 22ęž‰54-56,63-71, Dioni 18ęž‰13-14,19-24)
\p 
\v 53 Kutupa Yesu mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you hali paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeme. Mo yeni peao haemeke haliweki make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliweki make mo tondiki haliweki make paeyao mombaęž‰la pitimikime.
\v 54 Pidamaęž‰ Yesu mo pate leke teli mea peekeme. Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ da mandane mandane hao yapenaęž‰ tukikinaęž‰ pua pitiekeme. Ipikaęž‰ loke titipu pinaęž‰yeke mo do handeteke haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± tinaęž‰ pitimikime.
\p 
\v 55 Yeni peao haemeke you haliweki make kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make Yesu lu homaaluekemaęž‰ potaęž‰ weimikipate otaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wimikime.
\v 56 Mo la halemeke haliwekimaęž‰ yayapiki pi la halemeke handaataęž‰ pi homeke na lemeke handaa na handaęž‰ wimikime.
\v 57 Kutupa mandane haliwekimaęž‰ tiao la halolo hataęž‰ yayapiki pi alotaęž‰
\v 58 Do halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo koto haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰emeke tembolo dataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hoeyaalueke leaęž‰eki opumaęž‰me laa Nate tepo paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ na aęž‰elo paęž‰laęž‰eki IĚ±maęž‰ aęž‰elueke leaęž‰eki opumaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 59 Koto lemekepate mo la halemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ pimanu alo hataęž‰ homeke pi kone na lemekeme.
\p 
\v 60 Kutupa yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ tiao mo haliweki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pea alotaęž‰ Pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lelipikipe. Koto haliwekimaęž‰ neke laaseme ekitaęž‰ eki haunaęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 61 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ pi na hondaęž‰ mea leke pa hayekeme.
\p Kutupa yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paa lotaęž‰ pea alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Ketiso yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 62 Yesumaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±e. Kutupa iki paeyaomaęž‰ mo hande Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo Wele Pitaęž‰laęž‰ Teke Halinaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ pitilieeki handilimikie leekeme. Kutupa ya nane koa tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ holaęž‰paniao ipilieeki handilimikie leekeme.
\v 63 Do pi opuaataęž‰ mo hande yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daumanu sinki pea alotaęž‰ Ekipeke la kitaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa mulumaęž‰pe.
\v 64 Do Kodaęž‰ laasaęž‰ pimanu opumaęž‰me. Eki hau puluekemaęž‰ hone witelemepe leekeme. Mo haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Lu homamanaęž‰ pipe lemekeme.
\p 
\v 65 Kutupa mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ dopi taataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke aęž‰mbao ipiki litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neke liaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki la kie lemekeme. Kutupa mo da handeteke haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ yombua baemekeme.
\s1 Pidamaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 26ęž‰69-75, Luku 22ęž‰56-62, Dioni 18ęž‰15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 66 Pidataęž‰ oni da mandane mandane hao tukikinaęž‰ pitinaęž‰ mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekinaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ e pokao hayeke wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰
\v 67 Pidamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke titipu pinaęž‰ pitiekeeki handaa pa wopu handolo alotaęž‰ Neke make mo Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± haepeme leekeme.
\v 68 Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± diaęž‰me. IĚ± mataęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ le pitaęž‰ eki epinaęž‰ lepe. IĚ± na handolome leekeme. Kutupa hama nane pua hayekeme. Koto kone kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ tiaaso hataęž‰ eĚ± leekeme.
\p 
\v 69 Hande e pokao hayeke wandikimaęž‰ Pida handaataęž‰ mo pambo haemeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paa alotaęž‰ Koto halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapakee leekeme.
\v 70 Koto leekepate Pidamaęž‰ paa alotaęž‰ IĚ± diaęž‰me leekeme.
\p Hosiki hao wetepenaęž‰ mo hande pambo haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ paa alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake halie. Neketaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili hali yeke handaa lomaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 71 Koto lemekepate Pidamaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± hoeyaenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ opitolo haenaęž‰ alome laataęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aleme halitaęž‰ IĚ± na handolome leekeme.
\v 72 Kutupa koto kone mo kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ hoto yaapo peao tiaaso hataęž‰ eĚ± leekeme. Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ leekeeki hone wiekeme. Mo kokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ hoto yaapo peao aĚ±iĚ± na leke haenaęž‰ kone hoto tepo ya biki aęž‰mbao lo hoeyaalipikie leekeeki hone wiekeme. Kutupa Pidamaęž‰ koto leekeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ eĚ± wopu leekeme.
\c 15
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰1-2,11-14, Luku 23ęž‰1-5, Dioni 18ęž‰28-38)
\p 
\v 1 Da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make tondiki haliwekimaęž‰ make wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ make kaĚ±leĚ±sete haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ make pi hotimikime. Kutupa mo haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu tonkao mea Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pemekeme.
\v 2 Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini hali halepe leekeme. Yesumaęž‰ Pailedinaęž‰ pi hombo peaaso alotaęž‰ Koto aleme leekeme.
\v 3 Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ kiki maĚ±leke litolo Yesunaęž‰ pieke ekimanu pa laęž‰ mea tiaemekeme.
\v 4 Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu paa lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lelipikipe. Nakaęž‰ hau pu halaęž‰ ekimanu wopu paęž‰taęž‰ neke do laęž‰ mea tiaaseme handaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 5 Koto leekepate Yesumaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na leekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ penkili piekeme.
\s1 Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu linaęž‰ leekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰15-26, Luku 23ęž‰13-25, Dioni 18ęž‰39â€”19ęž‰16)
\p 
\v 6 Lombei Pupa Yapeeke natenaęž‰ ne pambao haemeke pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ honke laęž‰tiki pu haemeke tupaęž‰ dipula pitieke hali homeke honke lemeketaęž‰ da penaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ tapatiki pu hayekeme.
\v 7 Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ haliweki mandane ekimanu dipula da paęž‰taęž‰ pitimikime. Koto haliwekimaęž‰ kapomani paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ limiki pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali limikime. Kutupa iki ameĚ±leĚ± hali homeke ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Batabasi pitiekeme.
\v 8 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao wopumaęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa honke alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki paęž‰taęž‰ peao hale tupaęž‰ peae lemekeme.
\v 9 Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini hali tapawanope leekeme.
\v 10 Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pitolo hataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ mea hatuku epenaęž‰ lemeke ekitaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ hone wieke handaa leekeme.
\p 
\v 11 Koto leekepate mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu na tapake Batabasi tapawaenaęž‰ honke lape laa ti lemekeme.
\v 12 Kutupa Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie aleme halitaęž‰ eki peaanope leekeme.
\v 13 Haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ pa pi tanda pu alualu pitolo alotaęž‰ Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ homenaęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 14 Pailedimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ekipekepe. Eki hau paęž‰laęž‰pe leekepate pi pa daeyao tanda pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ homenaęž‰e lemekeme.
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ Pailedimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ Batabasi da tapawaeyekeme. Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ yombua baenaęž‰ laataęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao homaenaęž‰yeke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu mea haleekeme.
\s1 Yesu ki ki taemekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰27-31, Dioni 19ęž‰2-3)
\p 
\v 16 Dolo aęž‰ndeli miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kapomani tiekenaęž‰ da hama tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ Yesu hatuku pemekeme. Koto da bikitaęž‰ Paęž‰totiomo dae. Kutupa mandane dolo aęž‰ndeli miniki haemeke haliweki paeyao epenaęž‰ wi lemekeme.
\v 17 Haliwekimaęž‰ wepiki nono piki dau maęž‰ndaęž‰ meaataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ pambaemekeme. Kutupa tekeke hake alemanu meaataęž‰ hopaęž‰ hopaęž‰ liao ipikaęž‰ younaęž‰ pambaemekeme.
\v 18 Kutupa kikimaęž‰ salusi pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halio. Hao hapekee lemekeme.
\v 19 Kutupa dolomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you yumbaęž‰tiki pea ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dopi taatiki peaataęž‰ tumiki yotu hatiki pea ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki hau pitolo hataęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniatiki pimikime.
\v 20 Yesu makeao moneaotaęž‰ mo hande dau wepikieki holaęž‰ meataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ daumanu yamaemekeme. Kutupa aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao homaaluekemaęž‰ Yesu hama hatuku pemekeme.
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiao limikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰32-44, Luku 23ęž‰26-43, Dioni 19ęž‰17-27)
\p 
\v 21 Potaęž‰naęž‰ puaataęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ mandaęž‰hande pimikime. Mo halitaęž‰ Saitini da hali Saimonoe. Ipikitaęž‰ Aęž‰lekesaęž‰nda Lupasi yaapo ipilikaęž‰ ateke hayekeme. Dolo aęž‰ndeli miniki haemeke haliwekimaęž‰ mo hali meaataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti mea tiawaenaęž‰ lemekeme.
\p 
\v 22 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ mo Kolokoda alenaęž‰ hatuku pemekeme. Hali you holikimaęž‰ handeke alenaęž‰e. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kolokoda lemekeme.
\v 23 Koto alenaęž‰ waini ikalitaęž‰ mo mulamula ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ taapunaęž‰ apaęž‰tao Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ halemekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kiao na neekeme.
\v 24 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ Yesu tamendiaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daumanu telipuluekemaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ kase tupaęž‰ peaataęž‰ tombo wataeyeke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ dau miaęž‰tiki pimikime.
\p 
\v 25 Nate wenokonaęž‰ haenaęž‰ Yesu mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiaemekeme.
\v 26 Kutupa mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ pi dupa wape piekeme. Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini halie wape piekeme.
\v 27 Pake nepeke hali yaapo make Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiaemekeme. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ popeke nane kikinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoe nane kikinaęž‰ tamendiaemekeme.
\v 28 [Kutu pimiki ekitaęž‰ mo Baibolo buka paęž‰taęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaeyekeme dupae. Mo pi wieke ekimanu yambelemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰ halie hone wimikime wape paęž‰laęž‰me.]
\p 
\v 29 Potaęž‰naęž‰ lombei pupa pa pu yapemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu ki ta ta pu amboke wankeatiki pitolo alotaęž‰ Aha. Neketaęž‰ mo hande tembolo da IĚ±maęž‰ hoeyao hoto teponaęž‰ paa aęž‰elueke le hande halipe.
\v 30 Nakaęž‰ kone daęž‰ta mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ holaęž‰paęž‰niao epoe lemekeme.
\v 31 Kutupa mo yeni peao haemeke you haliwekimaęž‰ make mo wape pea walaęž‰tiki pu haemeke haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone Yesu kitaaso hataęž‰ hande lemeke tupaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mandane wandaęž‰hali daęž‰tatiki piekepate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone daęž‰taapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰
\v 32 Neketaęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Kini hali hande Ketiso haekenaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ koto aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ neke holepeleeki nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi otaęž‰ opulumeke lemekeme.
\s1 Yesu homeekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰45-56, Luku 23ęž‰44-49, Dioni 19ęž‰28-30)
\p 
\v 33 Nate you tikekenaęž‰ haenaęž‰ mo kenke paeyao timbaęž‰ laęž‰ pamba puaataęž‰ nate 3 okoloko (lekelo yopulaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰) paa paĚ±aĚ± piekeme.
\v 34 Nate 3 okoloko (lekelo yopulaęž‰ haenaęž‰) Yesumaęž‰ anekehapu wi la alotaęž‰ Eloi. Eloi. Lama saęž‰baęž‰kadani la alotaęž‰ doeki leekeme. Ya Kodaęž‰o. Ya Kodaęž‰o. IĚ± ekipeke yonkaęž‰laalepe leekeme.
\p 
\v 35 Ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali mandaneeki manumaęž‰ opua alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Elaidia wi alaęž‰me lemekeme.
\v 36 Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ anke hao pua waęž‰laęž‰mbimaęž‰ handeke ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ meaataęž‰ kake liki neke waini ikali tenke lao tumba pitinaęž‰ laa tumapunaęž‰ hapulao Yesumaęž‰ dodopo lenaęž‰ halaęž‰liaaso alotaęž‰ Hando hape. Elaidiamaęž‰ ipiki aęž‰pa hondaęž‰ miliepe. Handomanaęž‰e leekeme.
\v 37 Kutupa Yesumaęž‰ anekehapu wi laa otaęž‰ homeekeme.
\p 
\v 38 Yesu homeeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo tembolo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ hande tupele pieke dautaęž‰ oli holu nanemaęž‰ sinki peaalupuniaotaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ ualu piekeme.
\v 39 Kutupataęž‰ aęž‰ndeli miniki haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ opisa halimaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ leke popeleke nane hayekeme. Kutupa Yesunaęž‰ homeekeeki handolo alotaęž‰ Woo. Do halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me leekeme.
\p 
\v 40 Mandane wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ hosiki yolaęž‰taęž‰ pao hataęž‰ handeteke haemekeme. Koto wandaęž‰weki ameĚ±leĚ± Maęž‰kadala da wandaęž‰ Meti hayeketaęž‰ kutupa mo wetepe weki Diaęž‰mesi Diosepe hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰naęž‰ inkiki Meti make Salome make haemekeme.
\v 41 Yesutaęž‰ Kaęž‰lili nane hayeke pitaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoki nane teli mea pomu hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ne yankatiki pu haemekeme. Mandane wandaęž‰weki wopu make ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± Diutuseleme da aęž‰paataęž‰ koto alenaęž‰ haemekeme.
\s1 Yesu toko mea hoimikieki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 27ęž‰57-61, Luku 23ęž‰50-56, Dioni 19ęž‰38-42)
\p 
\v 42 Kutupa nate hondaęž‰ pambuluekemaęž‰ semoko da wape pitolo haenaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ pituluekemaęž‰ tiki tiki yao wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰ yeeke handaa
\v 43 Aęž‰taęž‰matia da hali Diosepe epeekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ epeke kaĚ±leĚ±sete hali hayeketaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki epenaęž‰yeke handeteke hayekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu hao puaataęž‰ Pailedi paęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ toko hondaęž‰ meonoe laa honke leekeme.
\v 44 Kutupa Pailedimaęž‰ Yesu ambaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me pi opuaataęž‰ penkilipaęž‰tia pomua mo hande aęž‰ndeli dolo miniki haemeke haliwekinaęž‰ opisa hali epenaęž‰ wi laęž‰ mea lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰ Yesu ambaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 45 Homeaęž‰me leekeeki opuaataęž‰ Diosepemaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ toko minaęž‰ leekeme.
\v 46 Diosepemaęž‰ epeke hakepiki dau seliapo hambaataęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ toko hondaęž‰ mea hande dau teĚ±liao tonka mea tiaa puaataęž‰ toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ piekeme. Toopi homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea petepete peatiki pua mo toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰mbeekeme.
\v 47 Maęž‰kadala da wandaęž‰ Metimaęž‰ make Diosepenaęž‰ inkiki Metimaęž‰ make Yesu ipikaęž‰ lapaęž‰ piekeeki handepekeme.
\c 16
\s1 Yesu paa tiaeyekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰1-8, Luku 24ęž‰1-12, Dioni 20ęž‰1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Kutupa Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Hoto Pilaęž‰ Nate welealo nane paeyeketaęž‰ Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Metimaęž‰ make Diaęž‰mesinaęž‰ inkiki Metimaęž‰ Salomemaęž‰ make Yesunaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ yankaalo poluekemaęž‰ senisi alemanu hambemekeme.
\v 2 Sande da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso siki nate opaęž‰laęž‰ haenaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ toko wieke ale paęž‰taęž‰ pemekeme.
\v 3 Pulu hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Mo hande toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰mba ulaęž‰ toopitaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyao petepete yawaliaęž‰pe lemekeme.
\v 4 Koto lemekepate pa handaęž‰liaaso hataęž‰ mo hande toopi petepete yawao lumbupa wieke ekitaęž‰ handemekeme. Kutupa make mo toopitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke yeekeme.
\v 5 Mo toopi lumba wieke alenaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambaataęž‰ weki hali homeke handemekeme. Mo wekihalitaęž‰ hakepiki dau hokulu pikieki pambaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ popeke nane kiki nane pitiekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰ manumaęž‰taęž‰ penkili pimikime.
\p 
\v 6 Mo hande wekihalimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Na penkili peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Naęž‰saęž‰tete hali Yesu mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wapepiki tinaęž‰ tamendiaemeke hali weitelememe. Ipikitaęž‰ do paęž‰taęž‰ na ulaęž‰me. Ambaęž‰ tiaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ toko wimiki alenaęž‰ koto handaęž‰pe leekeme.
\v 7 Kotoeki handaa Pupe laa Pida make Yesu ipikaęž‰ mandane disaipolo haliweki make Yesutaęž‰ mo Kaęž‰lili nane titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la peaęž‰me lolo pupe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande leaęž‰ tupaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ handilimikie lolo pupe leekeme.
\p 
\v 8 Mo wandaęž‰manu hama nane opolu bao mo toko wieke alenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laotaęž‰ pututu litolo hataęž‰ make penkili pitolo hataęž‰ pindi pa puaataęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homemeke handaa maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi na lemekeme.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Meti paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰9-10, Dioni 20ęž‰11-18)
\p 
\v 9 [Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ Sande da panake kaęž‰laęž‰polo haenaęž‰ tiaotaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la mo Maęž‰kadala wandaęž‰ Metimaęž‰ handenaęž‰yeke peneme yaeyekeme. Mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ hoke temoko watake hataęž‰ tolu lieke wandaęž‰e.
\v 10 Mo wandaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± ambaęž‰ pomu haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ eĚ± alo haenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ leeke pi lolo peekeme.
\v 11 Kutu piekepate mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Yesu paa tiao halaęž‰me leekeeki opuataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ handoaęž‰me leekeeki opua kone otaęž‰ na opimikime.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ disaipolo hali yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki waleekeeki
\r (Luku 24ęž‰13-35)
\p 
\v 12 Wetepenaęž‰ hali yaapo potaęž‰naęž‰ pepekepate Yesumaęž‰ mo hali yaapomaęž‰ handenaęž‰yeke taęž‰taęž‰ piki hali leke peekeme.
\v 13 Kutupa mo hali yaapomaęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la puaataęž‰ mandane hoki nane tolu haemeke wandaęž‰hali lolo pepekepate ipilikaęž‰ pi make na opimikime.
\s1 Yesumaęž‰ mo 11 disaipolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki waleekeeki
\r (Maęž‰tiu 28ęž‰16-20, Luku 24ęž‰36-49, Dioni 20ęž‰19-23, Aposolo 1ęž‰6-8)
\p 
\v 14 Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ mo hande kiki yaaponaęž‰ ankenaęž‰ homeke pu haliweki kone ne nalo pitinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone waleekeme. Yesumaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tiao hayekeeki handemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi na opimiki handaataęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo haliwekinaęž‰ pi na opimiki ekinaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ puki takaęž‰laeyeke ekinaęž‰ make pi leekeme.
\v 15 Yesumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ puaataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ do pi seliapo walaęž‰paęž‰peke laa
\v 16 Hali epimaęž‰ pi mea bapitaisi peawayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ daęž‰ta halieke. Kutu piliepate hali epimaęž‰ pi na miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yenki milieke. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi yokaalu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ alu pilieke.
\v 17 Kutupa pi mulu peleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ do wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu handilimikie leekeme. Ya bikinaęž‰ hoke temokomanu tolu limikie. Panake pimanu lelimikie.
\v 18 Hoke ketomanu kikimaęž‰ minilimikie. Hali homaasaęž‰ ikali nemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ na homilimikie. Yeni haaseme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiki wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali tiaalimikie leekeme.
\s1 Yesu oli ya nane hatuku miekeeki
\r (Luku 24ęž‰50-53, Aposolo 1ęž‰9-11)
\p 
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ Tekehali Yesumaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali pi la halo paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu mea oli ya nane hatuku miekeme. Kutupa Yesutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ popeke nane kiki nane pitiniaeyekeme.
\v 20 Yesutaęž‰ oli hepeni nane pua hataęž‰ disaipolo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kenke paeyaonaęž‰ do pi seliapo walaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme. Kutupa Tekehalimaęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ e pokolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi otaęž‰ pie lenaęž‰yeke wele pieke ekimanu pimikime. Kutu pimikime.] 
